in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTexMouth_ST.xy + _MainTexMouth_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DecalRoughness;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DecalMetal;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RenderType;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AlphaToMask;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _actorscale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _FurTilling;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Metallic;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Smoothness;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Cutoff;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _BumpScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _EmissionColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SketchHalftoneMin;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SketchHalftoneMax;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SketchColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RampThreshold;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RampSmooth;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AOScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ActorScaleAttribute;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _FurShape;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Rimlightoffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _viweoffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHshadow;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _RimLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MatMapMul;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHColorScale;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _FurTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
bool u_xlatb1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
vec4 u_xlat5;
vec2 u_xlat6;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
vec4 u_xlat9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
vec3 u_xlat10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_12;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
vec3 u_xlat15;
float u_xlat16;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_18;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_21;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_25;
mediump float u_xlat16_26;
float u_xlat29;
bool u_xlatb29;
float u_xlat30;
mediump float u_xlat16_35;
mediump float u_xlat16_42;
float u_xlat43;
float u_xlat44;
float u_xlat45;
mediump float u_xlat16_50;
mediump float u_xlat16_53;
mediump float u_xlat16_54;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_0.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_0.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat15.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat15.xyz, u_xlat15.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = texture(_FurTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat43 = u_xlat16_3.x * _SunShift;
    u_xlat43 = u_xlat43 * 0.5 + _SunShiftOffuse2;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat43) + vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_42 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_42 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_42);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_42) * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat43 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat43 = u_xlat43 * u_xlat43;
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_0.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_4.x = max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(u_xlat16_4.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat5.zw = u_xlat16_4.xx * vec2(_glossiness_2X, _glossiness_2Y);
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat5.zw * u_xlat5.zw;
    u_xlat43 = u_xlat43 / u_xlat6.x;
    u_xlat44 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz);
    u_xlat44 = u_xlat44 * u_xlat44;
    u_xlat45 = u_xlat44 / u_xlat6.y;
    u_xlat43 = u_xlat43 + u_xlat45;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_18.xy = u_xlat16_18.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_18.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_18.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.x = dot(u_xlat16_18.xyz, u_xlat16_18.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_7.x);
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xxx;
    u_xlat45 = dot(u_xlat16_18.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat43 = u_xlat45 * u_xlat45 + u_xlat43;
    u_xlat43 = u_xlat43 * u_xlat43;
    u_xlat5.xy = u_xlat16_4.xx * vec2(_glossiness_1X, _glossiness_1Y);
    u_xlat5 = u_xlat5.xyyw * u_xlat5.xyxz;
    u_xlat43 = u_xlat43 * u_xlat5.w;
    u_xlat43 = u_xlat43 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat43 = float(1.0) / u_xlat43;
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_3.x * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_7.x * _FurShape;
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_7.x * u_xlat16_3.y + 1.0;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat16_7.xx * vs_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat16_6 = texture(_MainTex, u_xlat6.xy);
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_0.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_21.x = u_xlat16_7.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_21.x = min(max(u_xlat16_21.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_21.x = clamp(u_xlat16_21.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_7.x = (-u_xlat16_7.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_7.x = (-u_xlat16_7.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_7.x = (-u_xlat16_4.x) + u_xlat16_7.x;
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_7.x + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_7.x = min(max(u_xlat16_7.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_7.x = clamp(u_xlat16_7.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-u_xlat16_6.xyz) * u_xlat16_21.xxx + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * _specularColor2.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat43) * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = max(u_xlat10.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat43 = u_xlat16_3.x * _SunShift + _SunShiftOffuse1;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat43) + vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_9.xyz, u_xlat16_9.xyz);
    u_xlat16_35 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat16_9.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x / u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat15.x = u_xlat44 / u_xlat5.y;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat15.x + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat45 * u_xlat45 + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat45 = u_xlat45;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat45 = min(max(u_xlat45, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat45 = clamp(u_xlat45, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat5.z;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * _specularColor1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = max(u_xlat1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat10.xyz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat45) * u_xlat45 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat15.x = u_xlat45 * u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat15.x * u_xlat15.x + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_35 / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat15.x = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_35 + 1.0;
    u_xlat15.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat15.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat29 = u_xlat16_4.x * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat29;
    u_xlat1.x = min(u_xlat1.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat44 = dot(u_xlat16_18.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat44 = min(max(u_xlat44, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat44 = clamp(u_xlat44, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat1.xzw * vec3(u_xlat44);
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat1.xzw * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = (-u_xlat1.xzw) * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005) + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat1.xzw * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * u_xlat16_21.xyz + u_xlat1.xzw;
    u_xlat1.xzw = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat1.xz,u_xlat1.w);
    u_xlat9.x = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xzw = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    vec3 txVec1 = vec3(u_xlat1.xz,u_xlat1.w);
    u_xlat9.y = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec1, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xzw = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    vec3 txVec2 = vec3(u_xlat1.xz,u_xlat1.w);
    u_xlat9.z = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec2, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xzw = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    vec3 txVec3 = vec3(u_xlat1.xz,u_xlat1.w);
    u_xlat9.w = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec3, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_50 = dot(u_xlat9, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_11.x = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_50 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_11.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb1 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb1 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb29 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb29 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb1 = u_xlatb29 || u_xlatb1;
    u_xlat16_50 = (u_xlatb1) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_50;
    u_xlat1.xzw = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_50) * u_xlat1.xzw;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_53 = (-_RampSmooth) * 0.5 + _RampThreshold;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat44 * u_xlat16_50 + (-u_xlat16_53);
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat44) * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_54 = _RampSmooth * 0.5 + _RampThreshold;
    u_xlat29 = (-u_xlat16_53) + u_xlat16_54;
    u_xlat29 = float(1.0) / u_xlat29;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat29 * u_xlat1.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.x = min(max(u_xlat1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat29 = u_xlat1.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_53 = dot(vec2(u_xlat29), u_xlat1.xx);
    u_xlat16_53 = u_xlat16_53 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_53 = u_xlat16_3.x + u_xlat16_53;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_53 = min(max(u_xlat16_53, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_53 = clamp(u_xlat16_53, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = (-_SketchColor.xyz) + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_53) * u_xlat16_13.xyz + _SketchColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = min(u_xlat16_11.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.x = u_xlat16_50 + _SHshadow;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_11.x = min(max(u_xlat16_11.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_11.x = clamp(u_xlat16_11.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_25.x = dot((-u_xlat2.xyz), u_xlat16_18.xyz);
    u_xlat16_25.x = u_xlat16_25.x + u_xlat16_25.x;
    u_xlat16_25.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xyz * (-u_xlat16_25.xxx) + (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_12.x = dot(u_xlat16_18.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_12.x = abs(u_xlat16_12.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_12.x = min(u_xlat16_12.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_26 = (-u_xlat16_4.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_26 = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_26;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_4.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_26 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_2 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_25.xyz, u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_2.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_4.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = exp2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_25.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_0.z));
    u_xlat16_26 = u_xlat16_0.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_26 = u_xlat16_26 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_4.x = exp2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(u_xlat16_4.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_25.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * u_xlat16_25.xyz;
    u_xlat15.xyz = u_xlat15.xxx * u_xlat16_25.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = (-u_xlat5.xyz) + u_xlat16_7.xxx;
    u_xlat44 = (-u_xlat16_12.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_7.x = (-u_xlat16_12.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_25.x = u_xlat44 * u_xlat44;
    u_xlat16_25.x = u_xlat16_25.x * u_xlat16_25.x;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_25.xxx * u_xlat2.xyz + u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat15.xyz = u_xlat15.xyz * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_18.y * u_xlat16_18.y;
    u_xlat16 = u_xlat16_18.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat2.x * 0.125 + u_xlat16;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat16);
    u_xlat2.y = u_xlat2.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat30 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_25.xy = max(u_xlat2.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_25.xy = u_xlat16_25.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_12.xzw = u_xlat16_25.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_25.xyz = u_xlat16_25.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xzw;
    u_xlat16_25.xyz = u_xlat16_25.xyz * _SHColorScale.xyz;
    u_xlat16_25.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * u_xlat16_25.xyz;
    u_xlat15.xyz = u_xlat16_25.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat15.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xxx + u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_8.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_8.x);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.x = dot(u_xlat16_18.xyz, u_xlat16_8.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_8.x = min(max(u_xlat16_8.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_8.x = clamp(u_xlat16_8.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xxx * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = max(u_xlat16_8.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = min(u_xlat16_8.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat15.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_8.x = (-u_xlat1.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_8.x = u_xlat16_7.x * u_xlat16_8.x + u_xlat15.x;
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_7.x / u_xlat16_8.x;
    u_xlat16_8.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_8.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_8.x);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.x = dot(u_xlat16_8.xyz, u_xlat16_18.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_18.x = min(max(u_xlat16_18.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_18.x = clamp(u_xlat16_18.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_7.x * u_xlat16_4.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_18.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_18.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_18.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_4.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat16_18.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_50 * u_xlat16_18.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_18.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_6.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat16_18.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_26) * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat16_6.w;
    return;
}

    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat13.xxx * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = max(u_xlat1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat21.xyz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat13.x = (-u_xlat8.x) * u_xlat8.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_43 = u_xlat16_28.x * u_xlat16_28.x;
    u_xlat26 = u_xlat16_43 * u_xlat8.x;
    u_xlat13.x = u_xlat26 * u_xlat26 + u_xlat13.x;
    u_xlat13.x = u_xlat16_43 / u_xlat13.x;
    u_xlat26 = u_xlat16_43 * u_xlat16_43 + 1.0;
    u_xlat26 = float(1.0) / u_xlat26;
    u_xlat13.x = u_xlat13.x * u_xlat13.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_28.x * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat13.x = u_xlat13.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat13.x = min(u_xlat13.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat10_9.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_42) * u_xlat1.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat13.xxx * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat8.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = (-u_xlat8.xyz) * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005) + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat8.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat10_13.zzz * u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_42 = dot((-u_xlat7.xyz), u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_42 + u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * (-vec3(u_xlat16_42)) + (-u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat16_42 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat16_42 = abs(u_xlat16_42) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_42 = min(u_xlat16_42, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_43 = (-u_xlat16_28.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_43 = u_xlat16_28.x * u_xlat16_43;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_28.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat16_28.x = u_xlat16_43 * 6.0;
    u_xlat10_6 = textureCube(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_11.xyz, u_xlat16_28.x);
    u_xlat16_28.x = u_xlat10_6.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_28.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_28.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_28.x = max(u_xlat16_28.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_28.x = log2(u_xlat16_28.x);
    u_xlat16_28.x = u_xlat16_28.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_28.x = exp2(u_xlat16_28.x);
    u_xlat16_28.x = u_xlat16_28.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat10_6.xyz * u_xlat16_28.xxx;
    u_xlat16_28.x = log2(abs(u_xlat10_5.z));
    u_xlat16_43 = u_xlat10_5.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_43 = u_xlat16_43 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_28.x = u_xlat16_28.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_28.x = exp2(u_xlat16_28.x);
    u_xlat16_28.x = min(u_xlat16_28.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_28.xxx * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat13.xyz = vec3(u_xlat26) * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = (-u_xlat1.xyz) + vec3(u_xlat16_41);
    u_xlat40 = (-u_xlat16_42) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_41 = (-u_xlat16_42) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat40 * u_xlat40;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_42 * u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_42) * u_xlat7.xyz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat13.xyz = u_xlat13.xyz * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_4.y * u_xlat16_4.y;
    u_xlat14.x = u_xlat16_4.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + u_xlat14.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat14.x);
    u_xlat1.y = u_xlat1.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat27 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_11.xy = max(u_xlat1.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_11.xy = u_xlat16_11.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_24.xyz = u_xlat16_11.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_24.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * _SHColorScale.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_28.xxx * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat13.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat13.xyz * u_xlat16_15.xxx + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_15.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_15.x);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_10.xyz);
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = max(u_xlat16_10.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = min(u_xlat16_10.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat13.x = u_xlat0.x * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_15.x = (-u_xlat0.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_41 * u_xlat16_15.x + u_xlat13.x;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_41 / u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat16_41 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_41 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_41);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_41) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_41 = dot(u_xlat16_10.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_41 = clamp(u_xlat16_41, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_28.x = u_xlat16_28.x * u_xlat16_41;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_28.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_28.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_28.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_28.x;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_28.x * u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_28.x = u_xlat16_15.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_28.x;
    u_xlat16_28.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_28.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat10_9.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat10_9.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = max(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));

    SV_Target0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_43) * u_xlat10_9.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat10_9.w;
    return;
}

in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTexMouth_ST.xy + _MainTexMouth_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightLerp;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightScale2;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _RimlightColor;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DecalRoughness;

#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _FurTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
vec4 u_xlat5;
vec4 u_xlat6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
vec4 u_xlat9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
vec3 u_xlat10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
vec3 u_xlat15;
float u_xlat16;
vec3 u_xlat17;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_18;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_21;
mediump float u_xlat16_25;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_26;
float u_xlat29;
bool u_xlatb29;
float u_xlat30;
mediump float u_xlat16_32;
mediump float u_xlat16_35;
mediump float u_xlat16_39;
mediump float u_xlat16_42;
float u_xlat43;
float u_xlat44;
bool u_xlatb44;
float u_xlat45;
mediump float u_xlat16_49;
mediump float u_xlat16_50;
mediump float u_xlat16_53;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_0.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_0.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat15.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat15.xyz, u_xlat15.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = texture(_FurTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat43 = u_xlat16_3.x * _SunShift;
    u_xlat43 = u_xlat43 * 0.5 + _SunShiftOffuse2;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat43) + vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_42 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_42 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_42);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_42) * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat43 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat43 = u_xlat43 * u_xlat43;
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_0.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_4.x = max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(u_xlat16_4.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat5.zw = u_xlat16_4.xx * vec2(_glossiness_2X, _glossiness_2Y);
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat5.zw * u_xlat5.zw;
    u_xlat43 = u_xlat43 / u_xlat6.x;
    u_xlat44 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz);
    u_xlat44 = u_xlat44 * u_xlat44;
    u_xlat45 = u_xlat44 / u_xlat6.y;
    u_xlat43 = u_xlat43 + u_xlat45;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_18.xy = u_xlat16_18.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_18.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_18.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.x = dot(u_xlat16_18.xyz, u_xlat16_18.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_7.x);
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xxx;
    u_xlat45 = dot(u_xlat16_18.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat43 = u_xlat45 * u_xlat45 + u_xlat43;
    u_xlat43 = u_xlat43 * u_xlat43;
    u_xlat5.xy = u_xlat16_4.xx * vec2(_glossiness_1X, _glossiness_1Y);
    u_xlat5 = u_xlat5.xyyw * u_xlat5.xyxz;
    u_xlat43 = u_xlat43 * u_xlat5.w;
    u_xlat43 = u_xlat43 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat43 = float(1.0) / u_xlat43;
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_3.x * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_7.x * _FurShape;
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_7.x * u_xlat16_3.y + 1.0;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat16_7.xx * vs_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat6 = texture(_MainTex, u_xlat6.xy);
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_0.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_21.x = u_xlat16_7.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_21.x = min(max(u_xlat16_21.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_21.x = clamp(u_xlat16_21.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_7.x = (-u_xlat16_7.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_7.x = (-u_xlat16_7.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_7.x = (-u_xlat16_4.x) + u_xlat16_7.x;
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_7.x + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_7.x = min(max(u_xlat16_7.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_7.x = clamp(u_xlat16_7.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-u_xlat6.xyz) * u_xlat16_21.xxx + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * _specularColor2.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat43) * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = max(u_xlat10.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat43 = u_xlat16_3.x * _SunShift + _SunShiftOffuse1;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat43) + vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_9.xyz, u_xlat16_9.xyz);
    u_xlat16_35 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat16_9.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x / u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat15.x = u_xlat44 / u_xlat5.y;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat15.x + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat45 * u_xlat45 + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat45 = u_xlat45;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat45 = min(max(u_xlat45, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat45 = clamp(u_xlat45, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat5.z;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * _specularColor1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = max(u_xlat1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat10.xyz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat45) * u_xlat45 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat15.x = u_xlat45 * u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat15.x * u_xlat15.x + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_35 / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat15.x = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_35 + 1.0;
    u_xlat15.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat15.x;
    u_xlat29 = u_xlat16_4.x * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat16_4.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.xw = u_xlat1.xw * u_xlat1.xw;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat29;
    u_xlat1.x = min(u_xlat1.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat10.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_18.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.x = min(max(u_xlat1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat10.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat10.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = u_xlat10.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = (-u_xlat10.xyz) * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005) + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = u_xlat10.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * u_xlat16_21.xyz + u_xlat10.xyz;
    u_xlat17.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat17.xy,u_xlat17.z);
    u_xlat9.x = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat17.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    vec3 txVec1 = vec3(u_xlat17.xy,u_xlat17.z);
    u_xlat9.y = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec1, 0.0);
    u_xlat17.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    vec3 txVec2 = vec3(u_xlat17.xy,u_xlat17.z);
    u_xlat9.z = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec2, 0.0);
    u_xlat17.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    vec3 txVec3 = vec3(u_xlat17.xy,u_xlat17.z);
    u_xlat9.w = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec3, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat9, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_50 = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_50;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb29 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb29 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb44 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb44 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb29 = u_xlatb29 || u_xlatb44;
    u_xlat16_4.x = (u_xlatb29) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_50 = (-_RampSmooth) * 0.5 + _RampThreshold;
    u_xlat29 = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat16_4.x + (-u_xlat16_50);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_53 = _RampSmooth * 0.5 + _RampThreshold;
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat16_50) + u_xlat16_53;
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat29;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.x = min(max(u_xlat1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat29 = u_xlat1.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_50 = dot(vec2(u_xlat29), u_xlat1.xx);
    u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_50 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_3.x + u_xlat16_50;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_50 = min(max(u_xlat16_50, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_50 = clamp(u_xlat16_50, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = (-_SketchColor.xyz) + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_50) * u_xlat16_12.xyz + _SketchColor.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = min(u_xlat16_12.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xyz * u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat16_12.xyz + u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_4.x + _SHshadow;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_50 = min(max(u_xlat16_50, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_50 = clamp(u_xlat16_50, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_11.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_0.z));
    u_xlat16_25 = u_xlat16_0.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_25 = u_xlat16_25 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_11.x = u_xlat16_11.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_11.x = exp2(u_xlat16_11.x);
    u_xlat16_11.x = min(u_xlat16_11.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xxx * _GlossyEnvironmentColor.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat15.xxx * u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_39 = dot(u_xlat16_18.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_39 = abs(u_xlat16_39) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_39 = min(u_xlat16_39, 1.0);
    u_xlat2.x = (-u_xlat16_39) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_39 = (-u_xlat16_39) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_53 = u_xlat2.x * u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat16_53 = u_xlat16_53 * u_xlat16_53;
    u_xlat2.xyz = (-u_xlat5.xyz) + u_xlat16_7.xxx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_53) * u_xlat2.xyz + u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_18.y * u_xlat16_18.y;
    u_xlat16 = u_xlat16_18.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat2.x * 0.125 + u_xlat16;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat16);
    u_xlat2.y = u_xlat2.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat30 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_12.xy = max(u_xlat2.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_12.xy = u_xlat16_12.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_26.xyz = u_xlat16_12.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_26.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * _SHColorScale.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xxx * u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_50) + u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat16_49 = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_49 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_49);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_49) * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_49 = dot(u_xlat16_18.xyz, u_xlat16_8.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_49 = min(max(u_xlat16_49, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_49 = clamp(u_xlat16_49, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_49) * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = max(u_xlat16_8.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = min(u_xlat16_8.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.w * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_49 = (-u_xlat1.w) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_49 = u_xlat16_39 * u_xlat16_49 + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_49 = u_xlat16_39 / u_xlat16_49;
    u_xlat16_8.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_8.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_8.x);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.x = dot(u_xlat16_8.xyz, u_xlat16_18.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_18.x = min(max(u_xlat16_18.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_18.x = clamp(u_xlat16_18.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_11.x * u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_49 * u_xlat16_18.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_32 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_32 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_32;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_32 * u_xlat16_18.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3

#else
    u_xlat16_18.x = clamp(u_xlat16_18.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_32 = u_xlat16_18.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_18.x * u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_18.x * u_xlat16_32;
    u_xlat16_32 = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_32 + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat6.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat16_18.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));

    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_25) * u_xlat6.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;

    u_xlat26 = u_xlat20 * u_xlat16_48;

    u_xlat13 = u_xlat16_48 / u_xlat13;
    u_xlat26 = u_xlat16_48 * u_xlat16_48 + 1.0;
    u_xlat26 = float(1.0) / u_xlat26;
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat13 * u_xlat13;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_28.y * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat14.x = u_xlat16_28.y + 1.0;
    u_xlat14.x = u_xlat14.x * u_xlat14.x;
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat13 * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat13 = min(u_xlat13, 100.0);
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat8.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat1.xzw = vec3(u_xlat16_43) * u_xlat1.xzw + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xzw;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat7.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = (-u_xlat7.xyz) * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005) + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat7.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat10_13.zzz * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_4.y * u_xlat16_4.y;
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat16_4.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat39 = u_xlat0.x * 0.125 + u_xlat13;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat13);
    u_xlat0.y = u_xlat0.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat39 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_10.xy = max(u_xlat0.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_10.xy = u_xlat16_10.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_23.xyz = u_xlat16_10.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_23.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * _SHColorScale.xyz;
    u_xlat16_41 = log2(abs(u_xlat10_5.z));
    u_xlat16_43 = u_xlat10_5.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_43 = u_xlat16_43 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_41 * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_41 = exp2(u_xlat16_41);
    u_xlat16_41 = min(u_xlat16_41, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_41) * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_41) * _GlossyEnvironmentColor.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat26) * u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat39 = (-u_xlat16_28.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_28.x = (-u_xlat16_28.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_48 = u_xlat39 * u_xlat39;
    u_xlat16_48 = u_xlat16_48 * u_xlat16_48;
    u_xlat7.xyz = (-u_xlat1.xzw) + vec3(u_xlat16_42);
    u_xlat1.xzw = vec3(u_xlat16_48) * u_xlat7.xyz + u_xlat1.xzw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat1.xzw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_15.xxx + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_15.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_15.x);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_9.xyz);
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = max(u_xlat16_9.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = min(u_xlat16_9.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat14.x * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_15.x = (-u_xlat14.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_28.x * u_xlat16_15.x + u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_28.x / u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat16_28.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_28.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_28.x);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_28.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_28.x = dot(u_xlat16_9.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_28.x = clamp(u_xlat16_28.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_28.x = u_xlat16_41 * u_xlat16_28.x;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_28.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_28.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_28.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_28.x;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_28.x * u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_28.x = u_xlat16_15.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat16_28.x;
    u_xlat16_28.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_28.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat8.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat8.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz * u_xlat16_2.xxx;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = max(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = min(u_xlat16_2.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_43) * u_xlat8.xyz + u_xlat16_2.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * u_xlat1.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz / u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0 = u_xlat8;
    return;
}

in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTexMouth_ST.xy + _MainTexMouth_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightAttenuation;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _IfDecal;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DecalRoughness;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DecalMetal;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RenderType;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AlphaToMask;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _actorscale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _FurTilling;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Metallic;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Smoothness;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Cutoff;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _BumpScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _EmissionColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SketchHalftoneMin;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SketchHalftoneMax;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SketchColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RampThreshold;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RampSmooth;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AOScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ActorScaleAttribute;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _FurShape;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Rimlightoffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _viweoffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHshadow;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _RimLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MatMapMul;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHColorScale;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(6) uniform mediump sampler2D _FurTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
bool u_xlatb1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
vec4 u_xlat5;
vec4 u_xlat6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
vec4 u_xlat9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
vec3 u_xlat10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_12;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
vec3 u_xlat15;
float u_xlat16;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_18;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_21;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_25;
mediump float u_xlat16_26;
float u_xlat29;
bool u_xlatb29;
float u_xlat30;
mediump float u_xlat16_35;
mediump float u_xlat16_42;
float u_xlat43;
float u_xlat44;
float u_xlat45;
mediump float u_xlat16_50;
mediump float u_xlat16_53;
mediump float u_xlat16_54;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_0.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_0.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat15.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat15.xyz, u_xlat15.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = texture(_FurTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat43 = u_xlat16_3.x * _SunShift;
    u_xlat43 = u_xlat43 * 0.5 + _SunShiftOffuse2;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat43) + vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_42 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_42 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_42);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_42) * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat43 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat43 = u_xlat43 * u_xlat43;
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_0.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_4.x = max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(u_xlat16_4.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat5.zw = u_xlat16_4.xx * vec2(_glossiness_2X, _glossiness_2Y);
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat5.zw * u_xlat5.zw;
    u_xlat43 = u_xlat43 / u_xlat6.x;
    u_xlat44 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz);
    u_xlat44 = u_xlat44 * u_xlat44;
    u_xlat45 = u_xlat44 / u_xlat6.y;
    u_xlat43 = u_xlat43 + u_xlat45;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_18.xy = u_xlat16_18.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_18.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_18.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.x = dot(u_xlat16_18.xyz, u_xlat16_18.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_7.x);
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xxx;
    u_xlat45 = dot(u_xlat16_18.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat43 = u_xlat45 * u_xlat45 + u_xlat43;
    u_xlat43 = u_xlat43 * u_xlat43;
    u_xlat5.xy = u_xlat16_4.xx * vec2(_glossiness_1X, _glossiness_1Y);
    u_xlat5 = u_xlat5.xyyw * u_xlat5.xyxz;
    u_xlat43 = u_xlat43 * u_xlat5.w;
    u_xlat43 = u_xlat43 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat43 = float(1.0) / u_xlat43;
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_3.x * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_7.x * _FurShape;
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_7.x * u_xlat16_3.y + 1.0;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat16_7.xx * vs_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat6 = texture(_MainTex, u_xlat6.xy);
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_0.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_21.x = u_xlat16_7.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_21.x = min(max(u_xlat16_21.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_21.x = clamp(u_xlat16_21.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_7.x = (-u_xlat16_7.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_7.x = (-u_xlat16_7.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_7.x = (-u_xlat16_4.x) + u_xlat16_7.x;
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_7.x + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_7.x = min(max(u_xlat16_7.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_7.x = clamp(u_xlat16_7.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-u_xlat6.xyz) * u_xlat16_21.xxx + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * _specularColor2.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat43) * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = max(u_xlat10.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat43 = u_xlat16_3.x * _SunShift + _SunShiftOffuse1;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat43) + vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_9.xyz, u_xlat16_9.xyz);
    u_xlat16_35 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat16_9.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x / u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat15.x = u_xlat44 / u_xlat5.y;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat15.x + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat45 * u_xlat45 + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat45 = u_xlat45;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat45 = min(max(u_xlat45, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat45 = clamp(u_xlat45, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat5.z;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * _specularColor1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = max(u_xlat1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat10.xyz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat45) * u_xlat45 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat15.x = u_xlat45 * u_xlat16_35;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat15.x * u_xlat15.x + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_35 / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat15.x = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_35 + 1.0;
    u_xlat15.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat15.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat29 = u_xlat16_4.x * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat29;
    u_xlat1.x = min(u_xlat1.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat44 = dot(u_xlat16_18.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat44 = min(max(u_xlat44, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat44 = clamp(u_xlat44, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat1.xzw * vec3(u_xlat44);
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat1.xzw * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = (-u_xlat1.xzw) * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005) + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat1.xzw * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * u_xlat16_21.xyz + u_xlat1.xzw;
    u_xlat1.xzw = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat1.xz,u_xlat1.w);
    u_xlat9.x = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xzw = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    vec3 txVec1 = vec3(u_xlat1.xz,u_xlat1.w);
    u_xlat9.y = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec1, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xzw = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    vec3 txVec2 = vec3(u_xlat1.xz,u_xlat1.w);
    u_xlat9.z = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec2, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.xzw = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    vec3 txVec3 = vec3(u_xlat1.xz,u_xlat1.w);
    u_xlat9.w = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec3, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_50 = dot(u_xlat9, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_11.x = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_50 = u_xlat16_50 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_11.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb1 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb1 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb29 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb29 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb1 = u_xlatb29 || u_xlatb1;
    u_xlat16_50 = (u_xlatb1) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_50;
    u_xlat1.xzw = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_50) * u_xlat1.xzw;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_53 = (-_RampSmooth) * 0.5 + _RampThreshold;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat44 * u_xlat16_50 + (-u_xlat16_53);
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat44) * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_54 = _RampSmooth * 0.5 + _RampThreshold;
    u_xlat29 = (-u_xlat16_53) + u_xlat16_54;
    u_xlat29 = float(1.0) / u_xlat29;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat29 * u_xlat1.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.x = min(max(u_xlat1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat29 = u_xlat1.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_53 = dot(vec2(u_xlat29), u_xlat1.xx);
    u_xlat16_53 = u_xlat16_53 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_53 = u_xlat16_3.x + u_xlat16_53;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_53 = min(max(u_xlat16_53, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_53 = clamp(u_xlat16_53, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = (-_SketchColor.xyz) + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_53) * u_xlat16_13.xyz + _SketchColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = min(u_xlat16_11.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.x = u_xlat16_50 + _SHshadow;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_11.x = min(max(u_xlat16_11.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_11.x = clamp(u_xlat16_11.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_25.x = dot((-u_xlat2.xyz), u_xlat16_18.xyz);
    u_xlat16_25.x = u_xlat16_25.x + u_xlat16_25.x;
    u_xlat16_25.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xyz * (-u_xlat16_25.xxx) + (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_12.x = dot(u_xlat16_18.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_12.x = abs(u_xlat16_12.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_12.x = min(u_xlat16_12.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_26 = (-u_xlat16_4.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_26 = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_26;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_4.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_26 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_2 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_25.xyz, u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_2.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_4.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = exp2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_25.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_0.z));
    u_xlat16_26 = u_xlat16_0.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_26 = u_xlat16_26 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_4.x = exp2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(u_xlat16_4.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_25.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * u_xlat16_25.xyz;
    u_xlat15.xyz = u_xlat15.xxx * u_xlat16_25.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = (-u_xlat5.xyz) + u_xlat16_7.xxx;
    u_xlat44 = (-u_xlat16_12.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_7.x = (-u_xlat16_12.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_25.x = u_xlat44 * u_xlat44;
    u_xlat16_25.x = u_xlat16_25.x * u_xlat16_25.x;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_25.xxx * u_xlat2.xyz + u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat15.xyz = u_xlat15.xyz * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_18.y * u_xlat16_18.y;
    u_xlat16 = u_xlat16_18.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat2.x * 0.125 + u_xlat16;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat16);
    u_xlat2.y = u_xlat2.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat30 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_25.xy = max(u_xlat2.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_25.xy = u_xlat16_25.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_12.xzw = u_xlat16_25.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_25.xyz = u_xlat16_25.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xzw;
    u_xlat16_25.xyz = u_xlat16_25.xyz * _SHColorScale.xyz;
    u_xlat16_25.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * u_xlat16_25.xyz;
    u_xlat15.xyz = u_xlat16_25.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat15.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xxx + u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_8.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_8.x);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.x = dot(u_xlat16_18.xyz, u_xlat16_8.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_8.x = min(max(u_xlat16_8.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_8.x = clamp(u_xlat16_8.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xxx * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = max(u_xlat16_8.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = min(u_xlat16_8.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat15.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_8.x = (-u_xlat1.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_8.x = u_xlat16_7.x * u_xlat16_8.x + u_xlat15.x;
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_7.x / u_xlat16_8.x;
    u_xlat16_8.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_8.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_8.x);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.x = dot(u_xlat16_8.xyz, u_xlat16_18.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_18.x = min(max(u_xlat16_18.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_18.x = clamp(u_xlat16_18.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_7.x * u_xlat16_4.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_18.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_18.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_18.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_4.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_18.x;
    u_xlat16_18.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_18.x = u_xlat16_50 * u_xlat16_18.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_18.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat6.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat16_18.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_18.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_26) * u_xlat6.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);

    u_xlat13.x = u_xlat13.x / u_xlat6.x;
    u_xlat26 = u_xlat46 / u_xlat6.y;

in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;

out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;

float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTexMouth_ST.xy + _MainTexMouth_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LODFade;
