#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _FurTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
float u_xlat0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_0;
uint u_xlatu0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
vec3 u_xlat10;
vec4 u_xlat11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
vec4 u_xlat12;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_14;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_15;
vec3 u_xlat16;
uint u_xlatu16;
vec3 u_xlat18;
mediump float u_xlat16_19;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_21;
float u_xlat32;
int u_xlati32;
bool u_xlatb32;
float u_xlat34;
mediump float u_xlat16_35;
float u_xlat48;
bool u_xlatb48;
float u_xlat50;
mediump float u_xlat16_51;
mediump float u_xlat16_52;
float u_xlat54;
mediump float u_xlat16_55;
float u_xlat56;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_FurTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_0.x * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * _FurShape;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_0.y + 1.0;
    u_xlat16.xz = u_xlat16_1.xx * vs_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_MainTex, u_xlat16.xz);
    u_xlat16_2 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_3.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_2.z));
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_3.x = exp2(u_xlat16_3.x);
    u_xlat16_19 = u_xlat16_2.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_2.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_3.z = max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_3.xz = min(u_xlat16_3.xz, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_51 = u_xlat16_2.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_51 = u_xlat16_51 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyw = u_xlat16_4.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyw;
    u_xlat16_52 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_52 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_52);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_52) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_5.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_5.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat16.x = dot(u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_5.xyz);
    u_xlat16.x = max(u_xlat16.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat16.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16.x);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16.xxx * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_52 = (-u_xlat16_19) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_52 = (-u_xlat16_52) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_19 = u_xlat16_19;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_19 = min(max(u_xlat16_19, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_19 = clamp(u_xlat16_19, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = (-u_xlat16_1.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_19) + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_19) * u_xlat8.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_19 = (-u_xlat16_3.z) + u_xlat16_52;
    u_xlat16_19 = u_xlat16_19 + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_19 = min(max(u_xlat16_19, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_19 = clamp(u_xlat16_19, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat16_3.z * u_xlat16_3.z;
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat16_52 * u_xlat16_52;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16.x = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat16.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16.x);
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat16.xxx * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat16.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16.x = min(max(u_xlat16.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16.x = clamp(u_xlat16.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = abs(u_xlat16_5.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_5.x = min(u_xlat16_5.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat50 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat54 = u_xlat50;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat54 = min(max(u_xlat54, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat54 = clamp(u_xlat54, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat2.x = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat2.x = min(max(u_xlat2.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat2.x = clamp(u_xlat2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat18.x = u_xlat16_4.y * u_xlat16_4.y;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat16_4.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat56 = u_xlat18.x * 0.125 + u_xlat34;
    u_xlat10.x = u_xlat56 + 0.125;
    u_xlat18.x = u_xlat18.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat34);
    u_xlat10.y = u_xlat18.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_21.xy = max(u_xlat10.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_21.xy = u_xlat16_21.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_21.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xyz * _SHColorScale.xyz;
    u_xlat18.x = (-u_xlat16_5.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_55 = u_xlat18.x * u_xlat18.x;
    u_xlat16_55 = u_xlat16_55 * u_xlat16_55;
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * _GlossyEnvironmentColor.xyz;
    u_xlat18.x = u_xlat16_52 * u_xlat16_52 + 1.0;
    u_xlat18.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat18.x;
    u_xlat10.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat18.xxx;
    u_xlat12.xyz = (-u_xlat8.xyz) + vec3(u_xlat16_19);
    u_xlat12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_55) * u_xlat12.xyz + u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = u_xlat10.xyz * u_xlat12.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_19 = (-_RampSmooth) * 0.5 + _RampThreshold;
    u_xlat16_55 = _RampSmooth * 0.5 + _RampThreshold;
    u_xlat18.x = (-u_xlat16_19) + u_xlat16_55;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat16.x + (-u_xlat16_19);
    u_xlat18.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat18.x;
    u_xlat18.x = u_xlat18.x * u_xlat34;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat18.x = min(max(u_xlat18.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat18.x = clamp(u_xlat18.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat18.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat18.x = u_xlat18.x * u_xlat18.x;
    u_xlat16_19 = dot(vec2(u_xlat34), u_xlat18.xx);
    u_xlat16_19 = u_xlat16_19 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_19 = u_xlat16_0.x + u_xlat16_19;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_19 = min(max(u_xlat16_19, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_19 = clamp(u_xlat16_19, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = (-_SketchColor.xyz) + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_19) * u_xlat16_11.xyz + _SketchColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat11.xy = u_xlat16_3.zz * vec2(_glossiness_1X, _glossiness_1Y);
    u_xlat11.zw = u_xlat16_3.zz * vec2(_glossiness_2X, _glossiness_2Y);
    u_xlat18.x = u_xlat16_0.x * _SunShift;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat16_0.x * _SunShift + _SunShiftOffuse1;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat0) + vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_19 = dot(u_xlat16_13.xyz, u_xlat16_13.xyz);
    u_xlat16_19 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_19);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_19) * u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat18.x * 0.5 + _SunShiftOffuse2;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat0) + vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_19 = dot(u_xlat16_14.xyz, u_xlat16_14.xyz);
    u_xlat16_19 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_19);
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_19) * u_xlat16_14.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * _specularColor1.xyz;
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat11.xyyw * u_xlat11.xyxz;
    u_xlat0 = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat16_13.xyz);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 * u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 / u_xlat12.x;
    u_xlat18.x = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz);
    u_xlat18.x = u_xlat18.x * u_xlat18.x;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat18.x / u_xlat12.y;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 + u_xlat34;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat50 * u_xlat50 + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 * u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 * u_xlat12.z;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat0 = float(1.0) / u_xlat0;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz * vec3(u_xlat0);
    u_xlat6.xyz = max(u_xlat6.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * _specularColor2.xyz;
    u_xlat12.xy = u_xlat11.zw * u_xlat11.zw;
    u_xlat0 = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat16_14.xyz);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 * u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 / u_xlat12.x;
    u_xlat18.x = u_xlat18.x / u_xlat12.y;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 + u_xlat18.x;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat50 * u_xlat50 + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 * u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 * u_xlat12.w;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat0 = float(1.0) / u_xlat0;
    u_xlat18.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * vec3(u_xlat0);
    u_xlat18.xyz = max(u_xlat18.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat18.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat0 = (-u_xlat54) * u_xlat54 + 1.0;
    u_xlat18.x = u_xlat16_52 * u_xlat54;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat18.x * u_xlat18.x + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat16_52 / u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 * u_xlat0;
    u_xlat18.x = u_xlat16_3.z * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 * u_xlat18.x;
    u_xlat0 = min(u_xlat0, 100.0);
    u_xlat18.xyz = vec3(u_xlat0) * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat18.xyz = u_xlat16.xxx * u_xlat18.xyz;
    u_xlat18.xyz = u_xlat18.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat18.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = (-u_xlat18.xyz) * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005) + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_0.zzz * u_xlat16_13.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = min(u_xlat16_21.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16.xxx * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xyz * u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xyz * u_xlat16_21.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_19 = _SHshadow + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_19 = min(max(u_xlat16_19, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_19 = clamp(u_xlat16_19, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat10.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_19) + u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat16_19 = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_19 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_19);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_19) * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_19 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_13.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_19 = min(max(u_xlat16_19, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_19 = clamp(u_xlat16_19, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_19) * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xyz * u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = max(u_xlat16_13.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = min(u_xlat16_13.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_19 = (-u_xlat16_5.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat16_3.z + 1.0;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 * u_xlat0;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat0 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_55 = (-u_xlat0) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_55 = u_xlat16_19 * u_xlat16_55 + u_xlat32;
    u_xlat16_19 = u_xlat16_19 / u_xlat16_55;
    u_xlat16_55 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_55 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_55);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_55) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_55 = dot(u_xlat16_13.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_55 = min(max(u_xlat16_55, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_55 = clamp(u_xlat16_55, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_55;
    u_xlat16_55 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_19 * u_xlat16_3.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_19 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_55;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_19 * u_xlat16_3.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_3.x = min(max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_19 = u_xlat16_3.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_19;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_1.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_14.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = max(u_xlat16_13.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = min(u_xlat16_13.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = vec3(u_xlat16_51) * u_xlat16_1.xyz + u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat16_21.x = min(_AdditionalLightsCount.x, unity_LightData.y);
    u_xlatu0 = uint(int(u_xlat16_21.x));
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat54 * u_xlat48 + (-u_xlat54);
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat32 * u_xlat54 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_21.x = u_xlat32 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat16_21.x = u_xlat32 * u_xlat16_21.x;
    u_xlat16_21.x = u_xlat48 / u_xlat16_21.x;
    u_xlat16_35 = (-u_xlat16_3.z) * u_xlat16_3.z + 1.0;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_35 + u_xlat16_52;
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat16.x * u_xlat16_35 + u_xlat16_52;
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16.x * u_xlat32 + u_xlat48;
    u_xlat16_35 = float(1.0) / float(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16.x = u_xlat16_35 * 0.5;
    u_xlat32 = (-u_xlat2.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat32 * u_xlat32;
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * u_xlat48;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat48 * u_xlat32;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat8.y * 50.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_35 = min(max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_35 = clamp(u_xlat16_35, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_52 = (-u_xlat32) * u_xlat48 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_5.xzw = u_xlat8.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_52);
    u_xlat16_5.xzw = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat2.xxx + u_xlat16_5.xzw;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16.x * u_xlat16_21.x;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat16_5.xzw + vec3(-6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = max(u_xlat16_5.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = min(u_xlat16_5.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * vec3(0.318309873, 0.318309873, 0.318309873) + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    for(uint u_xlatu_loop_1 = uint(0u) ; u_xlatu_loop_1<u_xlatu0 ; u_xlatu_loop_1++)
    {
        u_xlat32 = float(int(u_xlatu_loop_1));
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb48 = !!(u_xlat32<2.0);
#else
        u_xlatb48 = u_xlat32<2.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_13.xy = (bool(u_xlatb48)) ? unity_LightIndices[0].xy : unity_LightIndices[0].zw;
        u_xlat2.x = u_xlat32 + -2.0;
        u_xlat32 = (u_xlatb48) ? u_xlat32 : u_xlat2.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb32 = !!(u_xlat32<1.0);
#else
        u_xlatb32 = u_xlat32<1.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_35 = (u_xlatb32) ? u_xlat16_13.x : u_xlat16_13.y;
        u_xlati32 = int(u_xlat16_35);
        u_xlat2.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz) + _AdditionalLightsPosition[u_xlati32].xyz;
        u_xlat48 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
        u_xlat48 = max(u_xlat48, 6.10351563e-05);
        u_xlat50 = inversesqrt(u_xlat48);
        u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat50) * u_xlat2.xyz;
        u_xlat50 = float(1.0) / float(u_xlat48);
        u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati32].x + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati32].y;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat48 = min(max(u_xlat48, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat48 = clamp(u_xlat48, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * u_xlat50;
        u_xlat16_35 = dot(_AdditionalLightsSpotDir[u_xlati32].xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
        u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati32].z + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati32].w;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_35 = min(max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_35 = clamp(u_xlat16_35, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_35;
        u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * u_xlat16_35;
        u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_35 = min(max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_35 = clamp(u_xlat16_35, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_13.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * _AdditionalLightsColor[u_xlati32].xyz;
        u_xlat16_13.xyz = vec3(u_xlat48) * u_xlat16_13.xyz;
        u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_13.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    }
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat16_1.w;
    return;
}

    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);

    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);

    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;

void main()
{
    u_xlat10_0.xyz = texture2D(_FurTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat10_0.x * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_1 * _FurShape;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_1 * u_xlat10_0.y + 1.0;
    u_xlat16.xz = vec2(u_xlat16_1) * vs_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat10_1 = texture2D(_MainTex, u_xlat16.xz);
    u_xlat10_2 = texture2D(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_3.x = log2(abs(u_xlat10_2.z));
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * _AOScale;

	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_ProbesOcclusion;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SpecCube0_HDR;

	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_DynamicLightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAr;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBb;

#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;

in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTexMouth_ST.xy + _MainTexMouth_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _FurTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
float u_xlat0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_0;
uint u_xlatu0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
vec4 u_xlat10;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_10;
vec4 u_xlat11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_14;
vec3 u_xlat15;
uint u_xlatu15;
mediump float u_xlat16_18;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_20;
vec2 u_xlat21;
float u_xlat25;
float u_xlat30;
int u_xlati30;
bool u_xlatb30;
mediump float u_xlat16_33;
float u_xlat45;
bool u_xlatb45;
float u_xlat47;
mediump float u_xlat16_48;
mediump float u_xlat16_49;
float u_xlat51;
mediump float u_xlat16_52;
float u_xlat53;
float u_xlat54;
mediump float u_xlat16_57;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_FurTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_0.x * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * _FurShape;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_0.y + 1.0;
    u_xlat15.xz = u_xlat16_1.xx * vs_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_MainTex, u_xlat15.xz);
    u_xlat16_2 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_3.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_2.z));
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_3.x = exp2(u_xlat16_3.x);
    u_xlat16_18 = u_xlat16_2.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat16_2.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_3.z = max(u_xlat16_33, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_3.xz = min(u_xlat16_3.xz, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_48 = u_xlat16_2.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_48 = u_xlat16_48 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyw = u_xlat16_4.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyw;
    u_xlat16_49 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_49 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_49);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_49) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_5.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_5.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat15.x = dot(u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_5.xyz);
    u_xlat15.x = max(u_xlat15.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat15.x);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat15.xxx * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_49 = (-u_xlat16_18) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_49 = (-u_xlat16_49) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_18 = u_xlat16_18;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_18 = min(max(u_xlat16_18, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_18 = clamp(u_xlat16_18, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = (-u_xlat16_1.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_18) + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_18) * u_xlat8.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_18 = (-u_xlat16_3.z) + u_xlat16_49;
    u_xlat16_18 = u_xlat16_18 + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_18 = min(max(u_xlat16_18, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_18 = clamp(u_xlat16_18, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_49 = u_xlat16_3.z * u_xlat16_3.z;
    u_xlat45 = u_xlat16_49 * u_xlat16_49;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat15.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat15.x = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat15.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat15.x);
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat15.xxx * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat15.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat15.x = min(max(u_xlat15.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat15.x = clamp(u_xlat15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = abs(u_xlat16_5.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_5.x = min(u_xlat16_5.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat47 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat51 = u_xlat47;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat51 = min(max(u_xlat51, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat51 = clamp(u_xlat51, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat53 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat53 = min(max(u_xlat53, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat53 = clamp(u_xlat53, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat54 = u_xlat16_4.y * u_xlat16_4.y;
    u_xlat10.x = u_xlat16_4.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat25 = u_xlat54 * 0.125 + u_xlat10.x;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat25 + 0.125;
    u_xlat54 = u_xlat54 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat10.x);
    u_xlat11.y = u_xlat54 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_20.xy = max(u_xlat11.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_20.xy = u_xlat16_20.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_20.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = u_xlat16_20.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = u_xlat16_20.xyz * _SHColorScale.xyz;
    u_xlat16_52 = dot((-u_xlat2.xyz), u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat16_52 + u_xlat16_52;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * (-vec3(u_xlat16_52)) + (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat2.x = (-u_xlat16_5.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat2.x * u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat16_52 * u_xlat16_52;
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * u_xlat16_20.xyz;
    u_xlat16_57 = (-u_xlat16_3.z) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;

SubProgram "gles " {

"// hash: 2c03c96ddb695d1
#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
uniform 	mediump vec4 unity_WorldTransformParams;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainTexMouth_ST;
uniform 	mediump float _FurTilling;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTexMouth_ST.xy + _MainTexMouth_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

void main()
{
    u_xlat10_0.xyz = texture2D(_FurTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat10_0.x * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_1 * _FurShape;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_1 * u_xlat10_0.y + 1.0;
    u_xlat15.xz = vec2(u_xlat16_1) * vs_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat10_1 = texture2D(_MainTex, u_xlat15.xz);
    u_xlat10_2 = texture2D(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_3.x = log2(abs(u_xlat10_2.z));
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_3.x = exp2(u_xlat16_3.x);
    u_xlat16_18 = u_xlat10_2.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat10_2.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_3.z = max(u_xlat16_33, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_3.xz = min(u_xlat16_3.xz, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat10_2.xyz = texture2D(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat10_2.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_48 = u_xlat10_2.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_48 = u_xlat16_48 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyw = u_xlat16_4.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyw;
    u_xlat16_49 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_49 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_49);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_49) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_5.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_5.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat15.x = dot(u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_5.xyz);
    u_xlat15.x = max(u_xlat15.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat15.x);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat15.xxx * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_49 = (-u_xlat16_18) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_49 = (-u_xlat16_49) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_18 = u_xlat16_18;
    u_xlat16_18 = clamp(u_xlat16_18, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = (-u_xlat10_1.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_18) + u_xlat10_1.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat10_1.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_18) * u_xlat8.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_18 = (-u_xlat16_3.z) + u_xlat16_49;
    u_xlat16_18 = u_xlat16_18 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_18 = clamp(u_xlat16_18, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_49 = u_xlat16_3.z * u_xlat16_3.z;
    u_xlat45 = u_xlat16_49 * u_xlat16_49;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat15.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat15.x = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat15.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat15.x);
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat15.xxx * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat15.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat15.x = clamp(u_xlat15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = abs(u_xlat16_5.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_5.x = min(u_xlat16_5.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat47 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat51 = u_xlat47;
    u_xlat51 = clamp(u_xlat51, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat53 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat53 = clamp(u_xlat53, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat54 = u_xlat16_4.y * u_xlat16_4.y;
    u_xlat10.x = u_xlat16_4.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat25 = u_xlat54 * 0.125 + u_xlat10.x;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat25 + 0.125;
    u_xlat54 = u_xlat54 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat10.x);
    u_xlat11.y = u_xlat54 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_20.xy = max(u_xlat11.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_20.xy = u_xlat16_20.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_20.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = u_xlat16_20.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = u_xlat16_20.xyz * _SHColorScale.xyz;
    u_xlat16_52 = dot((-u_xlat2.xyz), u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat16_52 + u_xlat16_52;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * (-vec3(u_xlat16_52)) + (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat2.x = (-u_xlat16_5.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat2.x * u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat16_52 * u_xlat16_52;
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * u_xlat16_20.xyz;
    u_xlat16_57 = (-u_xlat16_3.z) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_57 = u_xlat16_3.z * u_xlat16_57;
    u_xlat16_57 = u_xlat16_57 * 6.0;
    u_xlat10_10 = textureCube(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_12.xyz, u_xlat16_57);
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat10_10.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_12.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_12.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_12.x = max(u_xlat16_12.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_12.x = log2(u_xlat16_12.x);
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_12.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_12.x = exp2(u_xlat16_12.x);
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_12.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat10_10.xyz * u_xlat16_12.xxx;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_49 * u_xlat16_49 + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * u_xlat2.xxx;
    u_xlat10.xyz = (-u_xlat8.xyz) + vec3(u_xlat16_18);
    u_xlat10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_52) * u_xlat10.xyz + u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * u_xlat10.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_20.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_18 = (-_RampSmooth) * 0.5 + _RampThreshold;
    u_xlat16_52 = _RampSmooth * 0.5 + _RampThreshold;
    u_xlat6.x = (-u_xlat16_18) + u_xlat16_52;
    u_xlat21.x = u_xlat15.x + (-u_xlat16_18);
    u_xlat6.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat6.x;
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat6.x * u_xlat21.x;
    u_xlat6.x = clamp(u_xlat6.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat21.x = u_xlat6.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat6.x * u_xlat6.x;
    u_xlat16_18 = dot(u_xlat21.xx, u_xlat6.xx);
    u_xlat16_18 = u_xlat16_18 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_18 = u_xlat10_0.x + u_xlat16_18;
    u_xlat16_18 = clamp(u_xlat16_18, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = (-_SketchColor.xyz) + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_18) * u_xlat16_12.xyz + _SketchColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = u_xlat16_20.xyz * u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xy = u_xlat16_3.zz * vec2(_glossiness_1X, _glossiness_1Y);
    u_xlat10.zw = u_xlat16_3.zz * vec2(_glossiness_2X, _glossiness_2Y);
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat10_0.x * _SunShift;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat10_0.x * _SunShift + _SunShiftOffuse1;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat0) + vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18 = dot(u_xlat16_12.xyz, u_xlat16_12.xyz);
    u_xlat16_18 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_18);
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_18) * u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat6.x * 0.5 + _SunShiftOffuse2;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat0) + vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18 = dot(u_xlat16_13.xyz, u_xlat16_13.xyz);
    u_xlat16_18 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_18);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_18) * u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * _specularColor1.xyz;
    u_xlat11 = u_xlat10.xyyw * u_xlat10.xyxz;
    u_xlat0 = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat16_12.xyz);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 * u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 / u_xlat11.x;
    u_xlat6.x = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz);
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat6.x * u_xlat6.x;
    u_xlat21.x = u_xlat6.x / u_xlat11.y;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 + u_xlat21.x;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat47 * u_xlat47 + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 * u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 * u_xlat11.z;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat0 = float(1.0) / u_xlat0;
    u_xlat11.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xyz * vec3(u_xlat0);
    u_xlat11.xyz = max(u_xlat11.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * _specularColor2.xyz;
    u_xlat21.xy = u_xlat10.zw * u_xlat10.zw;
    u_xlat0 = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat16_13.xyz);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 * u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 / u_xlat21.x;
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat6.x / u_xlat21.y;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 + u_xlat6.x;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat47 * u_xlat47 + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 * u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 * u_xlat11.w;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat0 = float(1.0) / u_xlat0;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * vec3(u_xlat0);
    u_xlat6.xyz = max(u_xlat6.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz + u_xlat11.xyz;
    u_xlat0 = (-u_xlat51) * u_xlat51 + 1.0;
    u_xlat47 = u_xlat16_49 * u_xlat51;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat47 * u_xlat47 + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat16_49 / u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 * u_xlat0;
    u_xlat47 = u_xlat16_3.z * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 * u_xlat47;
    u_xlat0 = min(u_xlat0, 100.0);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat0) * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat15.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = (-u_xlat6.xyz) * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005) + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat10_0.zzz * u_xlat16_12.xyz + u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = min(u_xlat16_20.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat15.xxx * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_20.xyz * u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * u_xlat16_20.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18 = _SHshadow + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_18 = clamp(u_xlat16_18, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_18) + u_xlat16_20.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18 = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_18 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_18);
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_18) * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_12.xyz);
    u_xlat16_18 = clamp(u_xlat16_18, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_18) * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_20.xyz * u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = max(u_xlat16_12.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = min(u_xlat16_12.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = u_xlat16_20.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_18 = (-u_xlat16_5.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat16_3.z + 1.0;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 * u_xlat0;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat0 * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_52 = (-u_xlat0) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat16_18 * u_xlat16_52 + u_xlat30;
    u_xlat16_18 = u_xlat16_18 / u_xlat16_52;
    u_xlat16_52 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_52 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_52);
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_52) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_52 = dot(u_xlat16_12.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_52 = clamp(u_xlat16_52, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_52;
    u_xlat16_52 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_18 * u_xlat16_3.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_18 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_52;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_18 * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_18 = u_xlat16_3.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_18;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat10_1.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat10_1.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_13.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = max(u_xlat16_12.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = min(u_xlat16_12.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = u_xlat16_20.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = vec3(u_xlat16_48) * u_xlat10_1.xyz + u_xlat16_20.xyz;
    u_xlat16_20.x = min(_AdditionalLightsCount.x, unity_LightData.y);
    u_xlati0 = int(u_xlat16_20.x);
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat51 * u_xlat45 + (-u_xlat51);
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat30 * u_xlat51 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_20.x = u_xlat30 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat16_20.x = u_xlat30 * u_xlat16_20.x;
    u_xlat16_20.x = u_xlat45 / u_xlat16_20.x;
    u_xlat16_33 = (-u_xlat16_3.z) * u_xlat16_3.z + 1.0;
    u_xlat30 = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_33 + u_xlat16_49;
    u_xlat45 = u_xlat15.x * u_xlat16_33 + u_xlat16_49;
    u_xlat45 = u_xlat45 * u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat15.x * u_xlat30 + u_xlat45;
    u_xlat15.x = 0.5 / u_xlat16_33;
    u_xlat30 = (-u_xlat53) + 1.0;
    u_xlat45 = u_xlat30 * u_xlat30;
    u_xlat45 = u_xlat45 * u_xlat45;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat45 * u_xlat30;
    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat8.y * 50.0;
    u_xlat16_33 = clamp(u_xlat16_33, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_49 = (-u_xlat30) * u_xlat45 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_5.xzw = u_xlat8.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_49);
    u_xlat16_5.xzw = vec3(u_xlat16_33) * u_xlat2.xxx + u_xlat16_5.xzw;
    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat15.x * u_xlat16_20.x;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_33) * u_xlat16_5.xzw + vec3(-6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = max(u_xlat16_5.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = min(u_xlat16_5.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * vec3(0.318309873, 0.318309873, 0.318309873) + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    for(int u_xlati_loop_1 = 0 ; u_xlati_loop_1<u_xlati0 ; u_xlati_loop_1++)
    {
        u_xlat30 = float(u_xlati_loop_1);
        u_xlatb45 = u_xlat30<2.0;
        u_xlat16_12.xy = (bool(u_xlatb45)) ? unity_LightIndices[0].xy : unity_LightIndices[0].zw;
        u_xlat2.x = u_xlat30 + -2.0;
        u_xlat30 = (u_xlatb45) ? u_xlat30 : u_xlat2.x;
        u_xlatb30 = u_xlat30<1.0;
        u_xlat16_33 = (u_xlatb30) ? u_xlat16_12.x : u_xlat16_12.y;
        u_xlati30 = int(u_xlat16_33);
        u_xlat2.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz) + _AdditionalLightsPositionDynamicIndex(u_xlati30).xyz;
        u_xlat45 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
        u_xlat45 = max(u_xlat45, 6.10351563e-05);
        u_xlat47 = inversesqrt(u_xlat45);
        u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat47) * u_xlat2.xyz;
        u_xlat47 = float(1.0) / u_xlat45;
        u_xlat45 = u_xlat45 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati30).x + _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati30).y;
        u_xlat45 = clamp(u_xlat45, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat45 = u_xlat45 * u_xlat47;
        u_xlat16_33 = dot(_AdditionalLightsSpotDirDynamicIndex(u_xlati30).xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
        u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat16_33 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati30).z + _AdditionalLightsAttenuationDynamicIndex(u_xlati30).w;
        u_xlat16_33 = clamp(u_xlat16_33, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat16_33 * u_xlat16_33;
        u_xlat45 = u_xlat45 * u_xlat16_33;
        u_xlat16_33 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
        u_xlat16_33 = clamp(u_xlat16_33, 0.0, 1.0);
        u_xlat16_12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_33) * _AdditionalLightsColorDynamicIndex(u_xlati30).xyz;
        u_xlat16_12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat45) * u_xlat16_12.xyz;
        u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_12.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    }
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat10_1.w;
    return;
}

in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTexMouth_ST.xy + _MainTexMouth_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

UNITY_BINDING(1) uniform UnityPerMaterial {

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;

#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _FurTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_0;
uint u_xlatu0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
mediump float u_xlat16_1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;

uint u_xlatu16;

mediump float u_xlat16_19;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_21;
float u_xlat32;
int u_xlati32;
bool u_xlatb32;
float u_xlat34;
mediump float u_xlat16_35;
float u_xlat48;
bool u_xlatb48;

mediump float u_xlat16_51;
mediump float u_xlat16_52;
float u_xlat54;
mediump float u_xlat16_55;
float u_xlat56;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_FurTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_0.x * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_1 * _FurShape;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_1 * u_xlat16_0.y + 1.0;
    u_xlat16.xz = vec2(u_xlat16_1) * vs_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat1 = texture(_MainTex, u_xlat16.xz);
    u_xlat16_2 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_3.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_2.z));
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_3.x = exp2(u_xlat16_3.x);
    u_xlat16_19 = u_xlat16_2.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_2.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_3.z = max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_3.xz = min(u_xlat16_3.xz, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_51 = u_xlat16_2.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_51 = u_xlat16_51 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyw = u_xlat16_4.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyw;
    u_xlat16_52 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_52 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_52);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_52) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_5.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_5.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat16.x = dot(u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_5.xyz);
    u_xlat16.x = max(u_xlat16.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat16.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16.x);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16.xxx * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_52 = (-u_xlat16_19) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_52 = (-u_xlat16_52) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_19 = u_xlat16_19;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_19 = min(max(u_xlat16_19, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_19 = clamp(u_xlat16_19, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = (-u_xlat1.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_19) + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_19) * u_xlat8.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_19 = (-u_xlat16_3.z) + u_xlat16_52;
    u_xlat16_19 = u_xlat16_19 + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_19 = min(max(u_xlat16_19, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_19 = clamp(u_xlat16_19, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat16_3.z * u_xlat16_3.z;
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat16_52 * u_xlat16_52;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat16.x = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat16.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16.x);
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat16.xxx * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat16.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16.x = min(max(u_xlat16.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16.x = clamp(u_xlat16.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = abs(u_xlat16_5.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_5.x = min(u_xlat16_5.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat50 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat54 = u_xlat50;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat54 = min(max(u_xlat54, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat54 = clamp(u_xlat54, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat2.x = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat2.x = min(max(u_xlat2.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat2.x = clamp(u_xlat2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat18.x = u_xlat16_4.y * u_xlat16_4.y;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat16_4.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat56 = u_xlat18.x * 0.125 + u_xlat34;
    u_xlat10.x = u_xlat56 + 0.125;
    u_xlat18.x = u_xlat18.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat34);
    u_xlat10.y = u_xlat18.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_21.xy = max(u_xlat10.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_21.xy = u_xlat16_21.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_21.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xyz * _SHColorScale.xyz;
    u_xlat18.x = (-u_xlat16_5.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_55 = u_xlat18.x * u_xlat18.x;
    u_xlat16_55 = u_xlat16_55 * u_xlat16_55;
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * _GlossyEnvironmentColor.xyz;
    u_xlat18.x = u_xlat16_52 * u_xlat16_52 + 1.0;
    u_xlat18.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat18.x;
    u_xlat10.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat18.xxx;
    u_xlat12.xyz = (-u_xlat8.xyz) + vec3(u_xlat16_19);
    u_xlat12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_55) * u_xlat12.xyz + u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = u_xlat10.xyz * u_xlat12.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_19 = (-_RampSmooth) * 0.5 + _RampThreshold;
    u_xlat16_55 = _RampSmooth * 0.5 + _RampThreshold;
    u_xlat18.x = (-u_xlat16_19) + u_xlat16_55;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat16.x + (-u_xlat16_19);
    u_xlat18.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat18.x;
    u_xlat18.x = u_xlat18.x * u_xlat34;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat18.x = min(max(u_xlat18.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat18.x = clamp(u_xlat18.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat18.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat18.x = u_xlat18.x * u_xlat18.x;
    u_xlat16_19 = dot(vec2(u_xlat34), u_xlat18.xx);
    u_xlat16_19 = u_xlat16_19 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_19 = u_xlat16_0.x + u_xlat16_19;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_19 = min(max(u_xlat16_19, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_19 = clamp(u_xlat16_19, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = (-_SketchColor.xyz) + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_19) * u_xlat16_11.xyz + _SketchColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat11.xy = u_xlat16_3.zz * vec2(_glossiness_1X, _glossiness_1Y);
    u_xlat11.zw = u_xlat16_3.zz * vec2(_glossiness_2X, _glossiness_2Y);
    u_xlat18.x = u_xlat16_0.x * _SunShift;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * _SunShift + _SunShiftOffuse1;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_19 = dot(u_xlat16_13.xyz, u_xlat16_13.xyz);
    u_xlat16_19 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_19);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_19) * u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat18.x * 0.5 + _SunShiftOffuse2;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_19 = dot(u_xlat16_14.xyz, u_xlat16_14.xyz);
    u_xlat16_19 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_19);
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_19) * u_xlat16_14.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * _specularColor1.xyz;
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat11.xyyw * u_xlat11.xyxz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat16_13.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x / u_xlat12.x;
    u_xlat18.x = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz);
    u_xlat18.x = u_xlat18.x * u_xlat18.x;
    u_xlat34 = u_xlat18.x / u_xlat12.y;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x + u_xlat34;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat50 * u_xlat50 + u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat12.z;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat0.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx;
    u_xlat6.xyz = max(u_xlat6.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * _specularColor2.xyz;
    u_xlat12.xy = u_xlat11.zw * u_xlat11.zw;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat16_14.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x / u_xlat12.x;
    u_xlat18.x = u_xlat18.x / u_xlat12.y;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x + u_xlat18.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat50 * u_xlat50 + u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat12.w;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat0.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat18.xyz = u_xlat16_13.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx;
    u_xlat18.xyz = max(u_xlat18.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat18.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = (-u_xlat54) * u_xlat54 + 1.0;
    u_xlat18.x = u_xlat16_52 * u_xlat54;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat18.x * u_xlat18.x + u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_52 / u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat18.x = u_xlat16_3.z * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat18.x;
    u_xlat0.x = min(u_xlat0.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat18.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat18.xyz = u_xlat16.xxx * u_xlat18.xyz;
    u_xlat18.xyz = u_xlat18.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat18.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = (-u_xlat18.xyz) * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005) + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_0.zzz * u_xlat16_13.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = min(u_xlat16_21.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = u_xlat16.xxx * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xyz * u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_14.xyz * u_xlat16_21.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_19 = _SHshadow + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_19 = min(max(u_xlat16_19, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_19 = clamp(u_xlat16_19, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat10.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_19) + u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat16_19 = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_19 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_19);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_19) * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_19 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_13.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_19 = min(max(u_xlat16_19, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_19 = clamp(u_xlat16_19, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_19) * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xyz * u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = max(u_xlat16_13.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = min(u_xlat16_13.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_19 = (-u_xlat16_5.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat16_3.z + 1.0;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat0.x * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_55 = (-u_xlat0.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_55 = u_xlat16_19 * u_xlat16_55 + u_xlat32;
    u_xlat16_19 = u_xlat16_19 / u_xlat16_55;
    u_xlat16_55 = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_55 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_55);
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_55) * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_55 = dot(u_xlat16_13.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_55 = min(max(u_xlat16_55, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_55 = clamp(u_xlat16_55, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_55;
    u_xlat16_55 = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_19 * u_xlat16_3.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_19 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_55;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_19 * u_xlat16_3.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_3.x = min(max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_3.x = clamp(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_19 = u_xlat16_3.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_3.x;
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_19;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_14.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat1.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_14.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = max(u_xlat16_13.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_13.xyz = min(u_xlat16_13.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_21.xyz = u_xlat16_21.xyz + u_xlat16_13.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = vec3(u_xlat16_51) * u_xlat1.xyz + u_xlat16_21.xyz;
    u_xlat16_21.x = min(_AdditionalLightsCount.x, unity_LightData.y);
    u_xlatu0 = uint(int(u_xlat16_21.x));
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat54 * u_xlat48 + (-u_xlat54);
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat32 * u_xlat54 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_21.x = u_xlat32 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat16_21.x = u_xlat32 * u_xlat16_21.x;
    u_xlat16_21.x = u_xlat48 / u_xlat16_21.x;
    u_xlat16_35 = (-u_xlat16_3.z) * u_xlat16_3.z + 1.0;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_35 + u_xlat16_52;
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat16.x * u_xlat16_35 + u_xlat16_52;
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * u_xlat16_5.x;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16.x * u_xlat32 + u_xlat48;
    u_xlat16_35 = float(1.0) / float(u_xlat16_35);
    u_xlat16.x = u_xlat16_35 * 0.5;
    u_xlat32 = (-u_xlat2.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat32 * u_xlat32;
    u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * u_xlat48;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat48 * u_xlat32;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat8.y * 50.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_35 = min(max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_35 = clamp(u_xlat16_35, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_52 = (-u_xlat32) * u_xlat48 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_5.xzw = u_xlat8.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_52);
    u_xlat16_5.xzw = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat2.xxx + u_xlat16_5.xzw;
    u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16.x * u_xlat16_21.x;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * u_xlat16_5.xzw + vec3(-6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05);
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = max(u_xlat16_5.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = min(u_xlat16_5.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * vec3(0.318309873, 0.318309873, 0.318309873) + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    for(uint u_xlatu_loop_1 = uint(0u) ; u_xlatu_loop_1<u_xlatu0 ; u_xlatu_loop_1++)
    {
        u_xlat32 = float(int(u_xlatu_loop_1));
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb48 = !!(u_xlat32<2.0);
#else
        u_xlatb48 = u_xlat32<2.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_13.xy = (bool(u_xlatb48)) ? unity_LightIndices[0].xy : unity_LightIndices[0].zw;
        u_xlat2.x = u_xlat32 + -2.0;
        u_xlat32 = (u_xlatb48) ? u_xlat32 : u_xlat2.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb32 = !!(u_xlat32<1.0);
#else
        u_xlatb32 = u_xlat32<1.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_35 = (u_xlatb32) ? u_xlat16_13.x : u_xlat16_13.y;
        u_xlati32 = int(u_xlat16_35);
        u_xlat2.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz) + _AdditionalLightsPosition[u_xlati32].xyz;
        u_xlat48 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
        u_xlat48 = max(u_xlat48, 6.10351563e-05);
        u_xlat50 = inversesqrt(u_xlat48);
        u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat50) * u_xlat2.xyz;
        u_xlat50 = float(1.0) / float(u_xlat48);
        u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati32].x + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati32].y;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat48 = min(max(u_xlat48, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat48 = clamp(u_xlat48, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * u_xlat50;
        u_xlat16_35 = dot(_AdditionalLightsSpotDir[u_xlati32].xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
        u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati32].z + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati32].w;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_35 = min(max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_35 = clamp(u_xlat16_35, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_35 = u_xlat16_35 * u_xlat16_35;
        u_xlat48 = u_xlat48 * u_xlat16_35;
        u_xlat16_35 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_35 = min(max(u_xlat16_35, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_35 = clamp(u_xlat16_35, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_13.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_35) * _AdditionalLightsColor[u_xlati32].xyz;
        u_xlat16_13.xyz = vec3(u_xlat48) * u_xlat16_13.xyz;
        u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_13.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    }
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);

    u_xlat1.xyz = min(u_xlat0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0 = u_xlat1;
    return;

    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;

    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;

void main()
{
    u_xlat10_0.xyz = texture2D(_FurTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat10_0.x * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_1 * _FurShape;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_1 * u_xlat10_0.y + 1.0;
    u_xlat16.xz = vec2(u_xlat16_1) * vs_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat1 = texture2D(_MainTex, u_xlat16.xz);
    u_xlat10_2 = texture2D(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);

uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS

in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTexMouth_ST.xy + _MainTexMouth_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _FurTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_0;
uint u_xlatu0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
mediump float u_xlat16_1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_5;
vec3 u_xlat6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
vec3 u_xlat8;
vec3 u_xlat9;
vec4 u_xlat10;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_10;
vec4 u_xlat11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_13;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_14;
vec3 u_xlat15;
uint u_xlatu15;
mediump float u_xlat16_18;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_20;
vec2 u_xlat21;
float u_xlat25;
float u_xlat30;
int u_xlati30;
bool u_xlatb30;
mediump float u_xlat16_33;
float u_xlat45;
bool u_xlatb45;
float u_xlat47;
mediump float u_xlat16_48;
mediump float u_xlat16_49;
float u_xlat51;
mediump float u_xlat16_52;
float u_xlat53;
float u_xlat54;
mediump float u_xlat16_57;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_FurTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_0.x * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_1 * _FurShape;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_1 * u_xlat16_0.y + 1.0;
    u_xlat15.xz = vec2(u_xlat16_1) * vs_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat1 = texture(_MainTex, u_xlat15.xz);
    u_xlat16_2 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_3.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_2.z));
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_3.x = exp2(u_xlat16_3.x);
    u_xlat16_18 = u_xlat16_2.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat16_2.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_3.z = max(u_xlat16_33, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_3.xz = min(u_xlat16_3.xz, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_48 = u_xlat16_2.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_48 = u_xlat16_48 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyw = u_xlat16_4.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyw;
    u_xlat16_49 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_49 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_49);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_49) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_5.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_5.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat15.x = dot(u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_5.xyz);
    u_xlat15.x = max(u_xlat15.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat15.x);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat15.xxx * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_49 = (-u_xlat16_18) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_49 = (-u_xlat16_49) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_18 = u_xlat16_18;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_18 = min(max(u_xlat16_18, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_18 = clamp(u_xlat16_18, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = (-u_xlat1.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_18) + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_18) * u_xlat8.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_18 = (-u_xlat16_3.z) + u_xlat16_49;
    u_xlat16_18 = u_xlat16_18 + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_18 = min(max(u_xlat16_18, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_18 = clamp(u_xlat16_18, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_49 = u_xlat16_3.z * u_xlat16_3.z;
    u_xlat45 = u_xlat16_49 * u_xlat16_49;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat15.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat15.x = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat15.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat15.x);
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat15.xxx * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat15.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat15.x = min(max(u_xlat15.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat15.x = clamp(u_xlat15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = abs(u_xlat16_5.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_5.x = min(u_xlat16_5.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat47 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat51 = u_xlat47;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat51 = min(max(u_xlat51, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat51 = clamp(u_xlat51, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat53 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat53 = min(max(u_xlat53, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat53 = clamp(u_xlat53, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat54 = u_xlat16_4.y * u_xlat16_4.y;
    u_xlat10.x = u_xlat16_4.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat25 = u_xlat54 * 0.125 + u_xlat10.x;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat25 + 0.125;
    u_xlat54 = u_xlat54 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat10.x);
    u_xlat11.y = u_xlat54 + 0.125;

{

    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTexMouth_ST.xy + _MainTexMouth_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

void main()
{
    u_xlat10_0.xyz = texture2D(_FurTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat10_0.x * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_1 * _FurShape;
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_1 * u_xlat10_0.y + 1.0;
    u_xlat15.xz = vec2(u_xlat16_1) * vs_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat1 = texture2D(_MainTex, u_xlat15.xz);
    u_xlat10_2 = texture2D(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_3.x = log2(abs(u_xlat10_2.z));
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_3.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_3.x = exp2(u_xlat16_3.x);
    u_xlat16_18 = u_xlat10_2.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat10_2.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_3.z = max(u_xlat16_33, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_3.xz = min(u_xlat16_3.xz, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat10_2.xyz = texture2D(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat10_2.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_48 = u_xlat10_2.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_48 = u_xlat16_48 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = u_xlat16_4.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyw = u_xlat16_4.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyw;
    u_xlat16_49 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_49 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_49);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_49) * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_5.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_5.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat15.x = dot(u_xlat16_5.xyz, u_xlat16_5.xyz);
    u_xlat15.x = max(u_xlat15.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat15.x);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat15.xxx * u_xlat16_5.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_49 = (-u_xlat16_18) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_49 = (-u_xlat16_49) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_18 = u_xlat16_18;
    u_xlat16_18 = clamp(u_xlat16_18, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = (-u_xlat1.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_18) + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_18) * u_xlat8.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_18 = (-u_xlat16_3.z) + u_xlat16_49;
    u_xlat16_18 = u_xlat16_18 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_18 = clamp(u_xlat16_18, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_49 = u_xlat16_3.z * u_xlat16_3.z;
    u_xlat45 = u_xlat16_49 * u_xlat16_49;
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat15.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat15.x = dot(u_xlat9.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat15.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat15.x);
    u_xlat9.xyz = u_xlat15.xxx * u_xlat9.xyz;
    u_xlat15.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat15.x = clamp(u_xlat15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_5.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_5.x = abs(u_xlat16_5.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_5.x = min(u_xlat16_5.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat47 = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat51 = u_xlat47;
    u_xlat51 = clamp(u_xlat51, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat53 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat9.xyz);
    u_xlat53 = clamp(u_xlat53, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat54 = u_xlat16_4.y * u_xlat16_4.y;
    u_xlat10.x = u_xlat16_4.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat25 = u_xlat54 * 0.125 + u_xlat10.x;
    u_xlat11.x = u_xlat25 + 0.125;
    u_xlat54 = u_xlat54 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat10.x);
    u_xlat11.y = u_xlat54 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_20.xy = max(u_xlat11.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_20.xy = u_xlat16_20.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_20.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = u_xlat16_20.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = u_xlat16_20.xyz * _SHColorScale.xyz;
    u_xlat16_52 = dot((-u_xlat2.xyz), u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat16_52 + u_xlat16_52;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * (-vec3(u_xlat16_52)) + (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat2.x = (-u_xlat16_5.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat2.x * u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat16_52 = u_xlat16_52 * u_xlat16_52;
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * u_xlat16_20.xyz;
    u_xlat16_57 = (-u_xlat16_3.z) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_57 = u_xlat16_3.z * u_xlat16_57;
    u_xlat16_57 = u_xlat16_57 * 6.0;
    u_xlat10_10 = textureCube(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_12.xyz, u_xlat16_57);
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat10_10.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_12.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_12.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_12.x = max(u_xlat16_12.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_12.x = log2(u_xlat16_12.x);
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_12.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_12.x = exp2(u_xlat16_12.x);
    u_xlat16_12.x = u_xlat16_12.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat10_10.xyz * u_xlat16_12.xxx;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xxx * u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_49 * u_xlat16_49 + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_12.xyz * u_xlat2.xxx;
    u_xlat10.xyz = (-u_xlat8.xyz) + vec3(u_xlat16_18);
    u_xlat10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_52) * u_xlat10.xyz + u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * u_xlat10.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_20.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_18 = (-_RampSmooth) * 0.5 + _RampThreshold;
    u_xlat16_52 = _RampSmooth * 0.5 + _RampThreshold;
    u_xlat6.x = (-u_xlat16_18) + u_xlat16_52;
    u_xlat21.x = u_xlat15.x + (-u_xlat16_18);
    u_xlat6.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat6.x;
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat6.x * u_xlat21.x;
    u_xlat6.x = clamp(u_xlat6.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat21.x = u_xlat6.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat6.x * u_xlat6.x;
    u_xlat16_18 = dot(u_xlat21.xx, u_xlat6.xx);
    u_xlat16_18 = u_xlat16_18 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_18 = u_xlat10_0.x + u_xlat16_18;
    u_xlat16_18 = clamp(u_xlat16_18, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = (-_SketchColor.xyz) + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_18) * u_xlat16_12.xyz + _SketchColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = u_xlat16_20.xyz * u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xy = u_xlat16_3.zz * vec2(_glossiness_1X, _glossiness_1Y);
    u_xlat10.zw = u_xlat16_3.zz * vec2(_glossiness_2X, _glossiness_2Y);
    u_xlat6.x = u_xlat10_0.x * _SunShift;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat10_0.x * _SunShift + _SunShiftOffuse1;

        u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xyz * u_xlat16_12.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;

    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);

{
