    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

#endif
#ifdef FRAGMENT
#version 300 es

precision highp float;
precision highp int;
#define HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS 1
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS

uniform 	float _SunShiftOffuse1;

#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ActorScaleAttribute;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _FurShape;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHshadow;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _RimLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MatMapMul;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHColorScale;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _FurTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
vec4 u_xlat5;
vec2 u_xlat6;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
vec3 u_xlat10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
vec3 u_xlat14;
float u_xlat15;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_17;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_20;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_22;
float u_xlat27;
float u_xlat28;
mediump float u_xlat16_33;
mediump float u_xlat16_39;
float u_xlat40;
float u_xlat41;
float u_xlat42;
mediump float u_xlat16_46;
mediump float u_xlat16_47;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_0.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_0.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat14.xyz, u_xlat14.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat14.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = texture(_FurTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat16_3.x * _SunShift;
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 * 0.5 + _SunShiftOffuse2;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat40) + vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_39 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_39 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat40 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 * u_xlat40;
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_0.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_4.x = max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(u_xlat16_4.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat5.zw = u_xlat16_4.xx * vec2(_glossiness_2X, _glossiness_2Y);
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat5.zw * u_xlat5.zw;
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 / u_xlat6.x;
    u_xlat41 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz);
    u_xlat41 = u_xlat41 * u_xlat41;
    u_xlat42 = u_xlat41 / u_xlat6.y;
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 + u_xlat42;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_17.xy = u_xlat16_17.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_17.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat16_17.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.x = dot(u_xlat16_17.xyz, u_xlat16_17.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_7.x);
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xxx;
    u_xlat42 = dot(u_xlat16_17.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat42 * u_xlat42 + u_xlat40;
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 * u_xlat40;
    u_xlat5.xy = u_xlat16_4.xx * vec2(_glossiness_1X, _glossiness_1Y);
    u_xlat5 = u_xlat5.xyyw * u_xlat5.xyxz;
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 * u_xlat5.w;
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat40 = float(1.0) / u_xlat40;
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_3.x * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_7.x * _FurShape;
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_7.x * u_xlat16_3.y + 1.0;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat16_7.xx * vs_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat16_6 = texture(_MainTex, u_xlat6.xy);
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_0.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_20.x = u_xlat16_7.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_20.x = min(max(u_xlat16_20.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_20.x = clamp(u_xlat16_20.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_7.x = (-u_xlat16_7.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_7.x = (-u_xlat16_7.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_7.x = (-u_xlat16_4.x) + u_xlat16_7.x;
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_7.x + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_7.x = min(max(u_xlat16_7.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_7.x = clamp(u_xlat16_7.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-u_xlat16_6.xyz) * u_xlat16_20.xxx + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * _specularColor2.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat40) * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = max(u_xlat10.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat16_3.x * _SunShift + _SunShiftOffuse1;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat40) + vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_33 = dot(u_xlat16_9.xyz, u_xlat16_9.xyz);
    u_xlat16_33 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_33);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_33) * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat16_9.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x / u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat14.x = u_xlat41 / u_xlat5.y;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat14.x + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat42 * u_xlat42 + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat42 = u_xlat42;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat42 = min(max(u_xlat42, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat42 = clamp(u_xlat42, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat5.z;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * _specularColor1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = max(u_xlat1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat10.xyz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat42) * u_xlat42 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat14.x = u_xlat42 * u_xlat16_33;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat14.x * u_xlat14.x + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_33 / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat14.x = u_xlat16_33 * u_xlat16_33 + 1.0;
    u_xlat14.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat14.x;
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat16_4.x * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat16_4.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.xw = u_xlat1.xw * u_xlat1.xw;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat27;
    u_xlat1.x = min(u_xlat1.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_20.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat10.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_17.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.x = min(max(u_xlat1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat10.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat10.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = u_xlat10.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = (-u_xlat10.xyz) * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005) + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = u_xlat10.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * u_xlat16_20.xyz + u_xlat10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = _RampSmooth * 0.5 + _RampThreshold;
    u_xlat16_47 = (-_RampSmooth) * 0.5 + _RampThreshold;
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat16_4.x + (-u_xlat16_47);
    u_xlat41 = u_xlat1.x + (-u_xlat16_47);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat27;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat41;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.x = min(max(u_xlat1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat1.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(vec2(u_xlat27), u_xlat1.xx);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_3.x + u_xlat16_4.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = (-_SketchColor.xyz) + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * u_xlat16_11.xyz + _SketchColor.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = min(u_xlat16_11.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = u_xlat16_20.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_20.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_0.z));
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_0.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_47 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_4.x = exp2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(u_xlat16_4.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * _GlossyEnvironmentColor.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat14.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.x = dot(u_xlat16_17.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_9.x = abs(u_xlat16_9.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_9.x = min(u_xlat16_9.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat2.x = (-u_xlat16_9.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_9.x = (-u_xlat16_9.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_22.x = u_xlat2.x * u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat16_22.x = u_xlat16_22.x * u_xlat16_22.x;
    u_xlat2.xyz = (-u_xlat5.xyz) + u_xlat16_7.xxx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xxx * u_xlat2.xyz + u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_17.y * u_xlat16_17.y;
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat16_17.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat28 = u_xlat2.x * 0.125 + u_xlat15;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat15);
    u_xlat2.y = u_xlat2.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat28 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_22.xy = max(u_xlat2.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_22.xy = u_xlat16_22.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_22.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xyz * _SHColorScale.xyz;
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * u_xlat16_22.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.x = _SHshadow + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_7.x = min(max(u_xlat16_7.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_7.x = clamp(u_xlat16_7.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xxx + u_xlat16_20.xyz;
    u_xlat16_46 = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_46 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_46);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_46) * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_46 = dot(u_xlat16_17.xyz, u_xlat16_8.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_46 = min(max(u_xlat16_46, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_46 = clamp(u_xlat16_46, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_46) * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = max(u_xlat16_8.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = min(u_xlat16_8.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.w * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_46 = (-u_xlat1.w) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_46 = u_xlat16_9.x * u_xlat16_46 + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_46 = u_xlat16_9.x / u_xlat16_46;
    u_xlat16_8.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_8.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_8.x);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_17.x = dot(u_xlat16_8.xyz, u_xlat16_17.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_17.x = min(max(u_xlat16_17.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_17.x = clamp(u_xlat16_17.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_46 * u_xlat16_4.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_17.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_17.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_17.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_4.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_6.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat16_17.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_47) * u_xlat16_6.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat16_6.w;
    return;
}

void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;

    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];

    gl_Position = u_xlat1;

    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;

    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;

    u_xlat16_9.x = (-u_xlat16_9.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_22.x = u_xlat2.x * u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat16_22.x = u_xlat16_22.x * u_xlat16_22.x;
    u_xlat2.xyz = (-u_xlat5.xyz) + u_xlat16_7.xxx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xxx * u_xlat2.xyz + u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_17.y * u_xlat16_17.y;
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat16_17.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat28 = u_xlat2.x * 0.125 + u_xlat15;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat15);
    u_xlat2.y = u_xlat2.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat28 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_22.xy = max(u_xlat2.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_22.xy = u_xlat16_22.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_22.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xyz * _SHColorScale.xyz;
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * u_xlat16_22.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.x = _SHshadow + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_7.x = clamp(u_xlat16_7.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xxx + u_xlat16_20.xyz;
    u_xlat16_46 = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_46 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_46);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_46) * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_46 = dot(u_xlat16_17.xyz, u_xlat16_8.xyz);
    u_xlat16_46 = clamp(u_xlat16_46, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_46) * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = max(u_xlat16_8.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = min(u_xlat16_8.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.w * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_46 = (-u_xlat1.w) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_46 = u_xlat16_9.x * u_xlat16_46 + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_46 = u_xlat16_9.x / u_xlat16_46;
    u_xlat16_8.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_8.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_8.x);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_17.x = dot(u_xlat16_8.xyz, u_xlat16_17.xyz);
    u_xlat16_17.x = clamp(u_xlat16_17.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_46 * u_xlat16_4.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_17.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_17.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_17.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_4.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat10_6.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat10_6.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat16_17.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_47) * u_xlat10_6.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat10_6.w;
    return;
}

#endif
"

in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTexMouth_ST.xy + _MainTexMouth_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;

in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
vec4 u_xlat5;
vec2 u_xlat6;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
vec3 u_xlat10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
vec3 u_xlat14;
float u_xlat15;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_17;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_20;
float u_xlat27;
float u_xlat28;
mediump float u_xlat16_33;
mediump float u_xlat16_39;
float u_xlat40;
float u_xlat41;
float u_xlat42;
mediump float u_xlat16_47;
mediump float u_xlat16_48;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_0.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_0.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat14.xyz, u_xlat14.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat14.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = texture(_FurTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat16_3.x * _SunShift;
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 * 0.5 + _SunShiftOffuse2;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat40) + vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_39 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_39 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat40 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);

SubProgram "gles " {
Keywords { "ENABLE_POST_TONE" "_DEBUG_OFF" "_IFFUR_ON" "_IFRAMP_OFF" "_SHTYPE_LERP" }
"// hash: 39b61604e3177fa4
#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
uniform 	mediump vec4 unity_WorldTransformParams;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainTexMouth_ST;
uniform 	mediump float _FurTilling;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTexMouth_ST.xy + _MainTexMouth_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

#endif
#ifdef FRAGMENT
#version 100

#ifdef GL_FRAGMENT_PRECISION_HIGH
    precision highp float;
#else
    precision mediump float;
#endif
precision highp int;
uniform 	float _SunShiftOffuse1;
uniform 	float _SunShiftOffuse2;
uniform 	float _SunShift;
uniform 	vec4 _specularColor1;
uniform 	float _glossiness_1X;
uniform 	float _glossiness_1Y;

uniform 	mediump float _Emissive;

uniform 	mediump vec4 _SHBotColor;

uniform lowp sampler2D _MainTex;
uniform lowp sampler2D _MixMap;
uniform lowp sampler2D _BumpMap;
uniform lowp samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
#define SV_Target0 gl_FragData[0]
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_0;
lowp vec4 u_xlat10_0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
lowp vec4 u_xlat10_2;
lowp vec3 u_xlat10_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
vec4 u_xlat5;
vec2 u_xlat6;
lowp vec4 u_xlat10_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
vec3 u_xlat10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
vec3 u_xlat14;
float u_xlat15;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_17;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_20;
float u_xlat27;
float u_xlat28;
mediump float u_xlat16_33;
mediump float u_xlat16_39;
float u_xlat40;
float u_xlat41;
float u_xlat42;
mediump float u_xlat16_47;
mediump float u_xlat16_48;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_0.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_0.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat14.xyz, u_xlat14.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat14.xyz;
    u_xlat10_3.xyz = texture2D(_FurTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat10_3.x * _SunShift;
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 * 0.5 + _SunShiftOffuse2;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat40) + vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_39 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_39 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat40 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 * u_xlat40;
    u_xlat10_0 = texture2D(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat10_0.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_4.x = max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(u_xlat16_4.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat5.zw = u_xlat16_4.xx * vec2(_glossiness_2X, _glossiness_2Y);
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat5.zw * u_xlat5.zw;
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 / u_xlat6.x;
    u_xlat41 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz);
    u_xlat41 = u_xlat41 * u_xlat41;
    u_xlat42 = u_xlat41 / u_xlat6.y;
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 + u_xlat42;
    u_xlat10_6.xyz = texture2D(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat10_6.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_17.xy = u_xlat16_17.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_17.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat16_17.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.x = dot(u_xlat16_17.xyz, u_xlat16_17.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_7.x);
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xxx;
    u_xlat42 = dot(u_xlat16_17.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat42 * u_xlat42 + u_xlat40;
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 * u_xlat40;
    u_xlat5.xy = u_xlat16_4.xx * vec2(_glossiness_1X, _glossiness_1Y);
    u_xlat5 = u_xlat5.xyyw * u_xlat5.xyxz;
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 * u_xlat5.w;
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat40 = float(1.0) / u_xlat40;
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat10_3.x * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_7.x * _FurShape;
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_7.x * u_xlat10_3.y + 1.0;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat16_7.xx * vs_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat10_6 = texture2D(_MainTex, u_xlat6.xy);
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat10_0.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_20.x = u_xlat16_7.x;
    u_xlat16_20.x = clamp(u_xlat16_20.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_7.x = (-u_xlat16_7.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_7.x = (-u_xlat16_7.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_7.x = (-u_xlat16_4.x) + u_xlat16_7.x;
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_7.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_7.x = clamp(u_xlat16_7.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-u_xlat10_6.xyz) * u_xlat16_20.xxx + u_xlat10_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * _specularColor2.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat40) * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = max(u_xlat10.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat10_3.x * _SunShift + _SunShiftOffuse1;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat40) + vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_33 = dot(u_xlat16_9.xyz, u_xlat16_9.xyz);
    u_xlat16_33 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_33);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_33) * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat16_9.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x / u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat14.x = u_xlat41 / u_xlat5.y;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat14.x + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat42 * u_xlat42 + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat42 = u_xlat42;
    u_xlat42 = clamp(u_xlat42, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat5.z;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * _specularColor1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = max(u_xlat1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat10.xyz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat42) * u_xlat42 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat14.x = u_xlat42 * u_xlat16_33;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat14.x * u_xlat14.x + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_33 / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat14.x = u_xlat16_33 * u_xlat16_33 + 1.0;
    u_xlat14.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat14.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat16_4.x * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat27;
    u_xlat1.x = min(u_xlat1.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat10_6.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_20.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat41 = dot(u_xlat16_17.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat41 = clamp(u_xlat41, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat1.xzw * vec3(u_xlat41);
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat1.xzw * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = (-u_xlat1.xzw) * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005) + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat1.xzw * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = u_xlat10_3.zzz * u_xlat16_20.xyz + u_xlat1.xzw;
    u_xlat16_47 = _RampSmooth * 0.5 + _RampThreshold;
    u_xlat16_9.x = (-_RampSmooth) * 0.5 + _RampThreshold;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_47 + (-u_xlat16_9.x);
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat41 + (-u_xlat16_9.x);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat41) * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat27;
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat1.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_47 = dot(vec2(u_xlat27), u_xlat1.xx);
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_47 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat10_3.x + u_xlat16_47;
    u_xlat16_47 = clamp(u_xlat16_47, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = (-_SketchColor.xyz) + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_47) * u_xlat16_11.xyz + _SketchColor.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xzw = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat1.xzw * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = min(u_xlat16_11.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = u_xlat16_20.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_20.xyz;
    u_xlat16_47 = dot((-u_xlat2.xyz), u_xlat16_17.xyz);
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_47 + u_xlat16_47;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xyz * (-vec3(u_xlat16_47)) + (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_47 = dot(u_xlat16_17.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_47 = abs(u_xlat16_47) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_47 = min(u_xlat16_47, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_48 = (-u_xlat16_4.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_48 = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_48;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_4.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_48 * 6.0;
    u_xlat10_2 = textureCube(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_9.xyz, u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat10_2.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_4.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = exp2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat10_2.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(abs(u_xlat10_0.z));
    u_xlat16_48 = u_xlat10_0.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_48 = u_xlat16_48 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_4.x = exp2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(u_xlat16_4.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat14.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = (-u_xlat5.xyz) + u_xlat16_7.xxx;
    u_xlat41 = (-u_xlat16_47) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_7.x = (-u_xlat16_47) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat41 * u_xlat41;
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_47 * u_xlat16_47;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_47) * u_xlat2.xyz + u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat14.xyz * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_17.y * u_xlat16_17.y;
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat16_17.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat28 = u_xlat2.x * 0.125 + u_xlat15;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat15);
    u_xlat2.y = u_xlat2.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat28 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_9.xy = max(u_xlat2.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_9.xy = u_xlat16_9.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_9.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * _SHColorScale.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat14.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.x = _SHshadow + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_8.x = clamp(u_xlat16_8.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = u_xlat14.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xxx + u_xlat16_20.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_8.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_8.x);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.x = dot(u_xlat16_17.xyz, u_xlat16_8.xyz);
    u_xlat16_8.x = clamp(u_xlat16_8.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xxx * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_20.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = max(u_xlat16_8.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = min(u_xlat16_8.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = u_xlat16_20.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat14.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_8.x = (-u_xlat1.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_8.x = u_xlat16_7.x * u_xlat16_8.x + u_xlat14.x;
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_7.x / u_xlat16_8.x;
    u_xlat16_8.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_8.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_8.x);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_17.x = dot(u_xlat16_8.xyz, u_xlat16_17.xyz);
    u_xlat16_17.x = clamp(u_xlat16_17.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_7.x * u_xlat16_4.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_17.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_17.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_17.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_4.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat10_6.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat10_6.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat16_17.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_20.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_48) * u_xlat10_6.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat10_6.w;
    return;
}

#else
#define UNITY_UNIFORM uniform
#endif
#define UNITY_SUPPORTS_UNIFORM_LOCATION 1
#if UNITY_SUPPORTS_UNIFORM_LOCATION
#define UNITY_LOCATION(x) layout(location = x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(binding = x, std140)
#else
#define UNITY_LOCATION(x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(std140)
#endif
uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(1) uniform UnityPerDraw {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LODFade;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_WorldTransformParams;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_LightData;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_LightIndices[2];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_ProbesOcclusion;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SpecCube0_HDR;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_DynamicLightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAr;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAg;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAb;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBr;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBg;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBb;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHC;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(0) uniform UnityPerMaterial {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTexMouth_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTexEye_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _FurTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _BumpMap_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _BaseColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Emissive;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RoughNessOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SpecularColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MetallicOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _NormalScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _EmisssionScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SSSScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SSSColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DetailScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHTopColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHBotColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _EnvScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MainlightAttenuation;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _InvRim;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _split3;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec3 _AddLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _AddlightColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _AddlightDarkcolor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightAttenuation;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightLerp;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightScale2;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _RimlightColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightAttenuation;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _IfDecal;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DecalRoughness;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DecalMetal;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RenderType;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AlphaToMask;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _actorscale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _FurTilling;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Metallic;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Smoothness;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Cutoff;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _BumpScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _EmissionColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SketchHalftoneMin;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SketchHalftoneMax;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SketchColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RampThreshold;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RampSmooth;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AOScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ActorScaleAttribute;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _FurShape;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Rimlightoffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _viweoffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHshadow;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _RimLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MatMapMul;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHColorScale;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTexMouth_ST.xy + _MainTexMouth_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

#endif
#ifdef FRAGMENT
#version 300 es

precision highp float;
precision highp int;
#define HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS 1
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
#define UNITY_UNIFORM
#else
#define UNITY_UNIFORM uniform
#endif
#define UNITY_SUPPORTS_UNIFORM_LOCATION 1
#if UNITY_SUPPORTS_UNIFORM_LOCATION
#define UNITY_LOCATION(x) layout(location = x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(binding = x, std140)
#else
#define UNITY_LOCATION(x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(std140)
#endif
uniform 	float _SunShiftOffuse1;
uniform 	float _SunShiftOffuse2;
uniform 	float _SunShift;
uniform 	vec4 _specularColor1;
uniform 	float _glossiness_1X;
uniform 	float _glossiness_1Y;
uniform 	vec4 _specularColor2;
uniform 	float _glossiness_2X;
uniform 	float _glossiness_2Y;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _GlossyEnvironmentColor;
uniform 	vec4 _MainLightPosition;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightColor;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(0) uniform UnityPerMaterial {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTexMouth_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTexEye_ST;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHBotColor;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _AddlightDarkcolor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightScale;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightLerp;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightScale2;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _RimlightColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightAttenuation;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _IfDecal;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DecalRoughness;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DecalMetal;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RenderType;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AlphaToMask;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _actorscale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _FurTilling;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Metallic;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Smoothness;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Cutoff;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _BumpScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _EmissionColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SketchHalftoneMin;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SketchHalftoneMax;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SketchColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RampThreshold;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RampSmooth;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AOScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ActorScaleAttribute;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _FurShape;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Rimlightoffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _viweoffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHshadow;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _RimLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MatMapMul;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHColorScale;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _FurTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
vec4 u_xlat5;
vec4 u_xlat6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
vec3 u_xlat10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
vec3 u_xlat14;
float u_xlat15;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_17;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_20;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_22;
float u_xlat27;
float u_xlat28;
mediump float u_xlat16_33;
mediump float u_xlat16_39;
float u_xlat40;
float u_xlat41;
float u_xlat42;
mediump float u_xlat16_46;
mediump float u_xlat16_47;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_0.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_0.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat14.xyz, u_xlat14.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat14.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = texture(_FurTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat16_3.x * _SunShift;
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 * 0.5 + _SunShiftOffuse2;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat40) + vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_39 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_39 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat40 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 * u_xlat40;
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_0.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_4.x = max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(u_xlat16_4.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat5.zw = u_xlat16_4.xx * vec2(_glossiness_2X, _glossiness_2Y);
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat5.zw * u_xlat5.zw;
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 / u_xlat6.x;
    u_xlat41 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz);
    u_xlat41 = u_xlat41 * u_xlat41;
    u_xlat42 = u_xlat41 / u_xlat6.y;
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 + u_xlat42;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_17.xy = u_xlat16_17.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_17.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat16_17.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.x = dot(u_xlat16_17.xyz, u_xlat16_17.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_7.x);
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xxx;
    u_xlat42 = dot(u_xlat16_17.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat42 * u_xlat42 + u_xlat40;
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 * u_xlat40;
    u_xlat5.xy = u_xlat16_4.xx * vec2(_glossiness_1X, _glossiness_1Y);
    u_xlat5 = u_xlat5.xyyw * u_xlat5.xyxz;
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 * u_xlat5.w;
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat40 = float(1.0) / u_xlat40;
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_3.x * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_7.x * _FurShape;
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_7.x * u_xlat16_3.y + 1.0;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat16_7.xx * vs_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat6 = texture(_MainTex, u_xlat6.xy);
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_0.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_20.x = u_xlat16_7.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_20.x = min(max(u_xlat16_20.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_20.x = clamp(u_xlat16_20.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_7.x = (-u_xlat16_7.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_7.x = (-u_xlat16_7.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_7.x = (-u_xlat16_4.x) + u_xlat16_7.x;
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_7.x + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_7.x = min(max(u_xlat16_7.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_7.x = clamp(u_xlat16_7.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-u_xlat6.xyz) * u_xlat16_20.xxx + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * _specularColor2.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat40) * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = max(u_xlat10.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat16_3.x * _SunShift + _SunShiftOffuse1;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat40) + vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_33 = dot(u_xlat16_9.xyz, u_xlat16_9.xyz);
    u_xlat16_33 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_33);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_33) * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat16_9.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x / u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat14.x = u_xlat41 / u_xlat5.y;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat14.x + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat42 * u_xlat42 + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat42 = u_xlat42;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat42 = min(max(u_xlat42, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat42 = clamp(u_xlat42, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat5.z;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * _specularColor1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = max(u_xlat1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat10.xyz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat42) * u_xlat42 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat14.x = u_xlat42 * u_xlat16_33;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat14.x * u_xlat14.x + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_33 / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat14.x = u_xlat16_33 * u_xlat16_33 + 1.0;
    u_xlat14.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat14.x;
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat16_4.x * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat16_4.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.xw = u_xlat1.xw * u_xlat1.xw;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat27;
    u_xlat1.x = min(u_xlat1.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_20.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat10.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_17.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.x = min(max(u_xlat1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat10.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat10.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = u_xlat10.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = (-u_xlat10.xyz) * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005) + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = u_xlat10.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);

    u_xlat16_47 = (-_RampSmooth) * 0.5 + _RampThreshold;
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat16_4.x + (-u_xlat16_47);
    u_xlat41 = u_xlat1.x + (-u_xlat16_47);

    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat27;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat41;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.x = min(max(u_xlat1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat1.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(vec2(u_xlat27), u_xlat1.xx);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_3.x + u_xlat16_4.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = (-_SketchColor.xyz) + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * u_xlat16_11.xyz + _SketchColor.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = min(u_xlat16_11.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = u_xlat16_20.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_20.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_0.z));
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_0.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_47 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_4.x = exp2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(u_xlat16_4.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * _GlossyEnvironmentColor.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat14.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.x = dot(u_xlat16_17.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_9.x = abs(u_xlat16_9.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_9.x = min(u_xlat16_9.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat2.x = (-u_xlat16_9.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_9.x = (-u_xlat16_9.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_22.x = u_xlat2.x * u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat16_22.x = u_xlat16_22.x * u_xlat16_22.x;
    u_xlat2.xyz = (-u_xlat5.xyz) + u_xlat16_7.xxx;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xxx * u_xlat2.xyz + u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_17.y * u_xlat16_17.y;
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat16_17.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat28 = u_xlat2.x * 0.125 + u_xlat15;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat15);
    u_xlat2.y = u_xlat2.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat28 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_22.xy = max(u_xlat2.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_22.xy = u_xlat16_22.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_22.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xyz * _SHColorScale.xyz;
    u_xlat16_22.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * u_xlat16_22.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_22.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.x = _SHshadow + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_7.x = min(max(u_xlat16_7.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_7.x = clamp(u_xlat16_7.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xxx + u_xlat16_20.xyz;

    u_xlat16_46 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_46);

    u_xlat16_46 = dot(u_xlat16_17.xyz, u_xlat16_8.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_46 = min(max(u_xlat16_46, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_46 = clamp(u_xlat16_46, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_46) * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = max(u_xlat16_8.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = min(u_xlat16_8.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.w * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_46 = (-u_xlat1.w) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_46 = u_xlat16_9.x * u_xlat16_46 + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_46 = u_xlat16_9.x / u_xlat16_46;
    u_xlat16_8.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_8.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_8.x);
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_17.x = dot(u_xlat16_8.xyz, u_xlat16_17.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_17.x = min(max(u_xlat16_17.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_17.x = clamp(u_xlat16_17.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_46 * u_xlat16_4.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_17.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_17.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_17.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_4.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat6.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;

    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_47) * u_xlat6.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);

    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz / u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = min(u_xlat1.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0 = u_xlat6;
    return;
}

#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;

attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;

attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;

vec4 u_xlat0;

float u_xlat13;
float u_xlat14;
void main()
{
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTexMouth_ST.xy + _MainTexMouth_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat2.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat2.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat14 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat14 = max(u_xlat14, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat14 = inversesqrt(u_xlat14);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat14) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat13 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);

}

    u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 * u_xlat40;

    u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 * u_xlat5.w;
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat40 = float(1.0) / u_xlat40;

    u_xlat13 = max(u_xlat13, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat13 = inversesqrt(u_xlat13);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat13 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat13) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

#endif

precision highp float;

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _FurTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
vec4 u_xlat5;
vec4 u_xlat6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_9;
vec3 u_xlat10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
vec3 u_xlat14;
float u_xlat15;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_17;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_20;
float u_xlat27;
float u_xlat28;
mediump float u_xlat16_33;
mediump float u_xlat16_39;
float u_xlat40;
float u_xlat41;
float u_xlat42;
mediump float u_xlat16_47;
mediump float u_xlat16_48;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_0.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_0.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat14.xyz, u_xlat14.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat14.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = texture(_FurTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat16_3.x * _SunShift;
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 * 0.5 + _SunShiftOffuse2;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat40) + vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_39 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_39 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_39);
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_39) * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat40 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 * u_xlat40;
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_0.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_4.x = max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(u_xlat16_4.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat5.zw = u_xlat16_4.xx * vec2(_glossiness_2X, _glossiness_2Y);
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat5.zw * u_xlat5.zw;
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 / u_xlat6.x;
    u_xlat41 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz);
    u_xlat41 = u_xlat41 * u_xlat41;
    u_xlat42 = u_xlat41 / u_xlat6.y;
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 + u_xlat42;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_17.xy = u_xlat16_17.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_17.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat16_17.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.x = dot(u_xlat16_17.xyz, u_xlat16_17.xyz);
    u_xlat16_7.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_7.x);
    u_xlat16_17.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xxx;
    u_xlat42 = dot(u_xlat16_17.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat42 * u_xlat42 + u_xlat40;
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 * u_xlat40;
    u_xlat5.xy = u_xlat16_4.xx * vec2(_glossiness_1X, _glossiness_1Y);
    u_xlat5 = u_xlat5.xyyw * u_xlat5.xyxz;
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 * u_xlat5.w;
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat40 = float(1.0) / u_xlat40;
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_3.x * 2.0 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_7.x * _FurShape;
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_7.x * u_xlat16_3.y + 1.0;
    u_xlat6.xy = u_xlat16_7.xx * vs_TEXCOORD0.xy;
    u_xlat6 = texture(_MainTex, u_xlat6.xy);
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_0.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_20.x = u_xlat16_7.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_20.x = min(max(u_xlat16_20.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_20.x = clamp(u_xlat16_20.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_7.x = (-u_xlat16_7.x) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_7.x = (-u_xlat16_7.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_7.x = (-u_xlat16_4.x) + u_xlat16_7.x;
    u_xlat16_7.x = u_xlat16_7.x + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_7.x = min(max(u_xlat16_7.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_7.x = clamp(u_xlat16_7.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-u_xlat6.xyz) * u_xlat16_20.xxx + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * _specularColor2.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat40) * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat10.xyz = max(u_xlat10.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat40 = u_xlat16_3.x * _SunShift + _SunShiftOffuse1;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz * vec3(u_xlat40) + vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_33 = dot(u_xlat16_9.xyz, u_xlat16_9.xyz);
    u_xlat16_33 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_33);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_33) * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat16_9.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x / u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat14.x = u_xlat41 / u_xlat5.y;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat14.x + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat42 * u_xlat42 + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat42 = u_xlat42;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat42 = min(max(u_xlat42, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat42 = clamp(u_xlat42, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat5.z;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * _specularColor1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = max(u_xlat1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat10.xyz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = (-u_xlat42) * u_xlat42 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_33 = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat14.x = u_xlat42 * u_xlat16_33;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat14.x * u_xlat14.x + u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_33 / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat14.x = u_xlat16_33 * u_xlat16_33 + 1.0;
    u_xlat14.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat14.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat16_4.x * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat27;
    u_xlat1.x = min(u_xlat1.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat16_20.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat41 = dot(u_xlat16_17.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat41 = min(max(u_xlat41, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat41 = clamp(u_xlat41, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat1.xzw * vec3(u_xlat41);
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat1.xzw * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = (-u_xlat1.xzw) * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005) + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xzw = u_xlat1.xzw * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * u_xlat16_20.xyz + u_xlat1.xzw;
    u_xlat16_47 = _RampSmooth * 0.5 + _RampThreshold;
    u_xlat16_9.x = (-_RampSmooth) * 0.5 + _RampThreshold;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_47 + (-u_xlat16_9.x);
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat41 + (-u_xlat16_9.x);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = vec3(u_xlat41) * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat27;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.x = min(max(u_xlat1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat1.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_47 = dot(vec2(u_xlat27), u_xlat1.xx);
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_47 + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_3.x + u_xlat16_47;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_47 = min(max(u_xlat16_47, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_47 = clamp(u_xlat16_47, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = (-_SketchColor.xyz) + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_47) * u_xlat16_11.xyz + _SketchColor.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xzw = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat1.xzw * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = min(u_xlat16_11.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = u_xlat16_20.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_20.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz + u_xlat16_20.xyz;
    u_xlat16_47 = dot((-u_xlat2.xyz), u_xlat16_17.xyz);
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_47 + u_xlat16_47;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xyz * (-vec3(u_xlat16_47)) + (-u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_47 = dot(u_xlat16_17.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat16_47 = abs(u_xlat16_47) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_47 = min(u_xlat16_47, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_48 = (-u_xlat16_4.x) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_48 = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_48;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat16_4.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_48 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_2 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_9.xyz, u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_2.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_4.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = max(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_4.x = exp2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat16_4.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_0.z));
    u_xlat16_48 = u_xlat16_0.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_48 = u_xlat16_48 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_4.x = u_xlat16_4.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_4.x = exp2(u_xlat16_4.x);
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(u_xlat16_4.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat14.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = (-u_xlat5.xyz) + u_xlat16_7.xxx;
    u_xlat41 = (-u_xlat16_47) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_7.x = (-u_xlat16_47) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat41 * u_xlat41;
    u_xlat16_47 = u_xlat16_47 * u_xlat16_47;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_47) * u_xlat2.xyz + u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat14.xyz * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_17.y * u_xlat16_17.y;
    u_xlat15 = u_xlat16_17.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat28 = u_xlat2.x * 0.125 + u_xlat15;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat15);
    u_xlat2.y = u_xlat2.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat28 + 0.125;

#endif

    u_xlat16_8.x = (-u_xlat1.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;

#else

#endif

    u_xlat1 = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_14) * u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = (-u_xlat1.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_14) + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat8.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_25) + (-u_xlat6.xyz);
    u_xlat8.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * u_xlat8.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * u_xlat8.xyz;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat16_0.y * u_xlat16_0.y;
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat16_0.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat36 = u_xlat32 * 0.125 + u_xlat33;
    u_xlat32 = u_xlat32 * 0.125 + (-u_xlat33);
    u_xlat8.y = u_xlat32 + 0.125;
    u_xlat8.x = u_xlat36 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_4.xy = max(u_xlat8.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xy = u_xlat16_4.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_4.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * _SHColorScale.xyz;
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat16_5.xxx * u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = _SHshadow + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.x = clamp(u_xlat16_4.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat32 = dot(u_xlat2.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat32 = inversesqrt(u_xlat32);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat32) * u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat2.xyz);
    u_xlat2.x = clamp(u_xlat2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat12 = (-u_xlat2.x) * u_xlat2.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_15.x * u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x * u_xlat2.x + u_xlat12;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat16_15.x / u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat12 = u_xlat16_34 * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat2.z = u_xlat16_34 + 1.0;
    u_xlat2.xz = u_xlat2.xz * u_xlat2.xz;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.x * u_xlat12;
    u_xlat2.x = min(u_xlat2.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat2.xyw = u_xlat2.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat33 = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat33 = clamp(u_xlat33, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat2.xyw = u_xlat2.xyw * vec3(u_xlat33);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = vec3(u_xlat33) * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = u_xlat2.xyw * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = u_xlat2.xyw * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat6.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_7.xyz = min(u_xlat16_7.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_9.xyz = u_xlat2.xyw * u_xlat16_7.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xyz * u_xlat16_7.xyz + u_xlat16_9.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyw = u_xlat3.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_15.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_15.x);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(u_xlat16_0.xyz, u_xlat16_15.xyz);
    u_xlat16_15.x = clamp(u_xlat16_15.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyw * u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = max(u_xlat16_15.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = min(u_xlat16_15.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyw = u_xlat16_4.xyw + u_xlat16_15.xyz;
    u_xlat2.x = u_xlat2.z * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_15.x = (-u_xlat2.z) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_15.x = u_xlat16_30 * u_xlat16_15.x + u_xlat2.x;
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_30 / u_xlat16_15.x;
    u_xlat16_15.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_15.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_15.x);
    u_xlat16_15.xyz = u_xlat16_15.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.x = dot(u_xlat16_15.xyz, u_xlat16_0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_0.x = clamp(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_5.x * u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_30 * u_xlat16_0.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_10.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_10.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_10.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_10.x * u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = clamp(u_xlat16_0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_10.x = u_xlat16_0.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * u_xlat16_0.x;
    u_xlat16_0.x = u_xlat16_0.x * u_xlat16_10.x;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_5.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat1.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_5.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * u_xlat16_0.xxx;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = max(u_xlat16_0.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = min(u_xlat16_0.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyw;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_24) * u_xlat1.xyz + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(1.12949991, 1.12949991, 1.12949991) + vec3(0.0299999993, 0.0299999993, 0.0299999993);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vec3(1.09350002, 1.09350002, 1.09350002) + vec3(0.589999974, 0.589999974, 0.589999974);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat3.xyz + vec3(0.0799999982, 0.0799999982, 0.0799999982);
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat2.xyz / u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = min(u_xlat2.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    SV_Target0 = u_xlat1;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}

Keywords { "_DEBUG_OFF" "_IFFUR_OFF" "_IFRAMP_OFF" "_SHTYPE_LERP" }
