	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _AddlightDarkcolor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightAttenuation;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightLerp;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightScale2;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _RimlightColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightAttenuation;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _IfDecal;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DecalRoughness;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DecalMetal;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RenderType;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AlphaToMask;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _actorscale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _FurTilling;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Metallic;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Smoothness;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Cutoff;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _BumpScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _EmissionColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SketchHalftoneMin;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SketchHalftoneMax;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SketchColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RampThreshold;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RampSmooth;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AOScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AddlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ActorScaleAttribute;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _FurShape;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Rimlightoffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _viweoffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHshadow;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 _RimLightDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MatMapMul;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHColorScale;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD8;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTexMouth_ST.xy + _MainTexMouth_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat1 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = u_xlat1.xy * vec2(vec2(_FurTilling, _FurTilling));
    gl_Position = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.xyw = (-u_xlat0.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat1.w = u_xlat2.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat3.xyz, u_xlat3.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.w = u_xlat2.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat3;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat1.zxy * u_xlat3.yzx;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.yzx * u_xlat3.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat2;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    vs_TEXCOORD8 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

#endif

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump samplerCube unity_SpecCube0;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMap;
UNITY_LOCATION(5) uniform mediump sampler2D _MixMap;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_0;
uint u_xlatu0;
vec3 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
bool u_xlatb1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
vec3 u_xlat5;
vec4 u_xlat6;
bool u_xlatb6;
vec3 u_xlat7;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
vec2 u_xlat9;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_9;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_10;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_11;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_12;
float u_xlat13;
uint u_xlatu13;
vec3 u_xlat14;
mediump float u_xlat16_15;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_17;
float u_xlat18;
vec3 u_xlat20;
float u_xlat26;
int u_xlati26;
bool u_xlatb26;
float u_xlat27;
mediump float u_xlat16_28;
mediump float u_xlat16_30;
float u_xlat33;
float u_xlat40;
mediump float u_xlat16_41;
mediump float u_xlat16_42;
mediump float u_xlat16_43;
float u_xlat44;
bool u_xlatb44;
float u_xlat45;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0 = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_1 = texture(_MixMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_2.x = log2(abs(u_xlat16_1.z));
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * _AOScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = exp2(u_xlat16_2.x);
    u_xlat16_15 = u_xlat16_1.x + _MetallicOffset;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_1.y + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_2.z = max(u_xlat16_28, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_2.xz = min(u_xlat16_2.xz, vec2(1.0, 1.0));
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = texture(_BumpMap, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.xy = u_xlat16_3.xy * vec2(vec2(_NormalScale, _NormalScale));
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_1.w * _EmisssionScale;
    u_xlat16_41 = u_xlat16_41 * _Emissive;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_3.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_3.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_42 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_42 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_42);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_42) * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_4.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_4.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_4.xyz, u_xlat16_4.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = max(u_xlat1.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat6.xy,u_xlat6.z);
    u_xlat6.x = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    vec3 txVec1 = vec3(u_xlat7.xy,u_xlat7.z);
    u_xlat6.y = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec1, 0.0);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    vec3 txVec2 = vec3(u_xlat7.xy,u_xlat7.z);
    u_xlat6.z = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec2, 0.0);
    u_xlat7.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    vec3 txVec3 = vec3(u_xlat7.xy,u_xlat7.z);
    u_xlat6.w = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec3, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_42 = dot(u_xlat6, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_43 = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat16_42 * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_43;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb44 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb44 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb6 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb6 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb44 = u_xlatb44 || u_xlatb6;
    u_xlat16_42 = (u_xlatb44) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat16_43 = (-u_xlat16_15) * 0.959999979 + 0.959999979;
    u_xlat16_43 = (-u_xlat16_43) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_15 = u_xlat16_15;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15 = min(max(u_xlat16_15, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15 = clamp(u_xlat16_15, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = (-u_xlat16_0.xyz) * vec3(u_xlat16_15) + u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat6.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz + vec3(-0.0399999991, -0.0399999991, -0.0399999991);
    u_xlat6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_15) * u_xlat6.xyz + vec3(0.0399999991, 0.0399999991, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_15 = (-u_xlat16_2.z) + u_xlat16_43;
    u_xlat16_15 = u_xlat16_15 + 1.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15 = min(max(u_xlat16_15, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15 = clamp(u_xlat16_15, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_43 = u_xlat16_2.z * u_xlat16_2.z;
    u_xlat44 = u_xlat16_43 * u_xlat16_43;
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + _MainLightPosition.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat7.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
    u_xlat1.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat1.x);
    u_xlat7.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat7.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat1.x = min(max(u_xlat1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat1.x = clamp(u_xlat1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_4.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat14.xyz);
    u_xlat16_4.x = abs(u_xlat16_4.x) + 0.00400000019;
    u_xlat16_4.x = min(u_xlat16_4.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat45 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat45 = min(max(u_xlat45, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat45 = clamp(u_xlat45, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat7.x = dot(u_xlat14.xyz, u_xlat7.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat7.x = min(max(u_xlat7.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat7.x = clamp(u_xlat7.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat20.x = u_xlat16_3.y * u_xlat16_3.y;
    u_xlat33 = u_xlat16_3.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat20.z = u_xlat20.x * 0.125 + u_xlat33;
    u_xlat20.x = u_xlat20.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat33);
    u_xlat9.xy = u_xlat20.zx + vec2(0.125, 0.125);
    u_xlat16_17.xy = max(u_xlat9.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_17.xy = u_xlat16_17.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_17.yyy * _SHBotColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xxx * _SHTopColor.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * _SHColorScale.xyz;
    u_xlat16_17.x = dot((-u_xlat14.xyz), u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_17.x + u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_3.xyz * (-u_xlat16_17.xxx) + (-u_xlat14.xyz);
    u_xlat14.x = (-u_xlat16_4.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat14.x * u_xlat14.x;
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_17.x * u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_30 = (-u_xlat16_2.z) * 0.699999988 + 1.70000005;
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_2.z * u_xlat16_30;
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_30 * 6.0;
    u_xlat16_9 = textureLod(unity_SpecCube0, u_xlat16_11.xyz, u_xlat16_30);
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_9.w + -1.0;
    u_xlat16_30 = unity_SpecCube0_HDR.w * u_xlat16_30 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_30 = max(u_xlat16_30, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_30 = log2(u_xlat16_30);
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_30 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.y;
    u_xlat16_30 = exp2(u_xlat16_30);
    u_xlat16_30 = u_xlat16_30 * unity_SpecCube0_HDR.x;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_9.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_30);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat14.x = u_xlat16_43 * u_xlat16_43 + 1.0;
    u_xlat14.x = float(1.0) / u_xlat14.x;
    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat14.xxx;
    u_xlat20.xyz = (-u_xlat6.xyz) + vec3(u_xlat16_15);
    u_xlat20.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xxx * u_xlat20.xyz + u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat14.xyz * u_xlat20.xyz;
    u_xlat14.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * u_xlat16_8.xyz + u_xlat14.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_42) * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat5.x = (-u_xlat45) * u_xlat45 + 1.0;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat16_43 * u_xlat45;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat18 * u_xlat18 + u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat16_43 / u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat5.x * u_xlat5.x;
    u_xlat18 = u_xlat16_2.z * 0.25 + 0.25;
    u_xlat5.x = u_xlat5.x * u_xlat18;
    u_xlat5.x = min(u_xlat5.x, 100.0);
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xxx * u_xlat6.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat5.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * _SpecularColor.xyz;
    u_xlat5.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * vec3(1.20000005, 1.20000005, 1.20000005);
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = min(u_xlat16_10.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat1.xxx * u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = u_xlat5.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_11.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_12.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15 = u_xlat16_42 + _SHshadow;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15 = min(max(u_xlat16_15, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15 = clamp(u_xlat16_15, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat14.xyz * vec3(u_xlat16_15) + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15 = dot(_AddLightDir.xyz, _AddLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_15);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_15) * _AddLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_11.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_15 = min(max(u_xlat16_15, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_15 = clamp(u_xlat16_15, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_15) * _AddlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = max(u_xlat16_11.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = min(u_xlat16_11.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_15 = (-u_xlat16_4.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat14.x = u_xlat16_2.z + 1.0;
    u_xlat14.x = u_xlat14.x * u_xlat14.x;
    u_xlat27 = u_xlat14.x * 0.125;
    u_xlat16_17.x = (-u_xlat14.x) * 0.125 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_17.x = u_xlat16_15 * u_xlat16_17.x + u_xlat27;
    u_xlat16_15 = u_xlat16_15 / u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_17.x = dot(_RimLightDir.xyz, _RimLightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat16_17.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_17.x);
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_17.xxx * _RimLightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat16_17.x = dot(u_xlat16_11.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_17.x = min(max(u_xlat16_17.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_17.x = clamp(u_xlat16_17.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_17.x = (-_RimlightScale) + _RimlightScale2;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_15 * u_xlat16_2.x + (-_RimlightScale);
    u_xlat16_15 = float(1.0) / u_xlat16_17.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_15 * u_xlat16_2.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_2.x = min(max(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_2.x = clamp(u_xlat16_2.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_15 = u_xlat16_2.x * -2.0 + 3.0;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_2.x * u_xlat16_15;
    u_xlat16_15 = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_15 = u_xlat16_42 * u_xlat16_15 + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_2.x = u_xlat16_15 * u_xlat16_2.x;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_12.xyz = (-_RimlightColor.xyz) * u_xlat16_0.xyz + _RimlightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = _RimlightColor.www * u_xlat16_12.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xxx * u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = max(u_xlat16_11.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_11.xyz = min(u_xlat16_11.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_10.xyz = u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_11.xyz;
    u_xlat16_2.xyw = vec3(u_xlat16_41) * u_xlat16_0.xyz + u_xlat16_10.xyz;
    u_xlat16_42 = min(_AdditionalLightsCount.x, unity_LightData.y);
    u_xlatu0 = uint(int(u_xlat16_42));
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat45 * u_xlat44 + (-u_xlat45);
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat13 * u_xlat45 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat13 * 3.14159274;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat13 * u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat16_42 = u_xlat44 / u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat16_28 = (-u_xlat16_2.z) * u_xlat16_2.z + 1.0;
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat16_4.x * u_xlat16_28 + u_xlat16_43;
    u_xlat26 = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat16_28 + u_xlat16_43;
    u_xlat26 = u_xlat26 * u_xlat16_4.x;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat13 + u_xlat26;
    u_xlat16_28 = float(1.0) / float(u_xlat16_28);
    u_xlat13 = u_xlat16_28 * 0.5;
    u_xlat26 = (-u_xlat7.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat26 * u_xlat26;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat14.x = u_xlat26 * u_xlat1.x;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat6.y * 50.0;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_28 = min(max(u_xlat16_28, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_28 = clamp(u_xlat16_28, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_4.x = (-u_xlat26) * u_xlat1.x + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat6.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xxx;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_28) * u_xlat14.xxx + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat13 * u_xlat16_42;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_28) * u_xlat16_4.xyz + vec3(-6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05, -6.10351563e-05);
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = max(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, vec3(100.0, 100.0, 100.0));
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz * vec3(0.318309873, 0.318309873, 0.318309873) + u_xlat16_4.xyz;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyw;
    for(uint u_xlatu_loop_1 = uint(0u) ; u_xlatu_loop_1<u_xlatu0 ; u_xlatu_loop_1++)
    {
        u_xlat26 = float(int(u_xlatu_loop_1));
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb1 = !!(u_xlat26<2.0);
#else
        u_xlatb1 = u_xlat26<2.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_10.xy = (bool(u_xlatb1)) ? unity_LightIndices[0].xy : unity_LightIndices[0].zw;
        u_xlat14.x = u_xlat26 + -2.0;
        u_xlat26 = (u_xlatb1) ? u_xlat26 : u_xlat14.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlatb26 = !!(u_xlat26<1.0);
#else
        u_xlatb26 = u_xlat26<1.0;
#endif
        u_xlat16_28 = (u_xlatb26) ? u_xlat16_10.x : u_xlat16_10.y;
        u_xlati26 = int(u_xlat16_28);
        u_xlat1.xyz = (-vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz) + _AdditionalLightsPosition[u_xlati26].xyz;
        u_xlat40 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat40 = max(u_xlat40, 6.10351563e-05);
        u_xlat5.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat40);
        u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * u_xlat5.xxx;
        u_xlat5.x = float(1.0) / float(u_xlat40);
        u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati26].x + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati26].y;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat40 = min(max(u_xlat40, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat40 = clamp(u_xlat40, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 * u_xlat5.x;
        u_xlat16_28 = dot(_AdditionalLightsSpotDir[u_xlati26].xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
        u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_28 * _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati26].z + _AdditionalLightsAttenuation[u_xlati26].w;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_28 = min(max(u_xlat16_28, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_28 = clamp(u_xlat16_28, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_28 = u_xlat16_28 * u_xlat16_28;
        u_xlat40 = u_xlat40 * u_xlat16_28;
        u_xlat16_28 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
        u_xlat16_28 = min(max(u_xlat16_28, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
        u_xlat16_28 = clamp(u_xlat16_28, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
        u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_28) * _AdditionalLightsColor[u_xlati26].xyz;
        u_xlat16_10.xyz = vec3(u_xlat40) * u_xlat16_10.xyz;
        u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_4.xyz * u_xlat16_10.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    }
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    SV_Target0.w = u_xlat16_0.w;
    return;
}

#endif

}

#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec4 _ScreenParams;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[4];

uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
uniform 	mediump vec4 _OutlineColor;
uniform 	mediump float _Offset;
uniform 	vec4 _lightDir;
uniform 	vec4 _ScreenResolution;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_COLOR0;
varying mediump float vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
float u_xlat6;
float u_xlat9;
float u_xlat10;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = 0.0;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = max(u_xlat9, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat9 = dot(_lightDir.xyz, _lightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * _lightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-_OutlineColor.xyz) + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat3.xyz + _OutlineColor.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * in_COLOR0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD1.w = 1.0;

    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_NORMAL0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_NORMAL0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xz = u_xlat0.yy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].xy * u_xlat0.xx + u_xlat3.xz;
    u_xlat0.xy = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].xy * u_xlat0.zz + u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat6 = dot(u_xlat0.xy, u_xlat0.xy);
    u_xlat6 = inversesqrt(u_xlat6);
    u_xlat0.xy = vec2(u_xlat6) * u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy / _ScreenParams.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy * _ScreenResolution.yy;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat6 = u_xlat1.y * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].w;
    u_xlat6 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].w * u_xlat1.x + u_xlat6;
    u_xlat6 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].w * u_xlat1.z + u_xlat6;
    u_xlat6 = u_xlat6 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].w;
    u_xlat0.xy = vec2(u_xlat6) * u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy * vec2(0.00462962966, 0.00462962966);
    u_xlat2.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[0].x;
    u_xlat2.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[1].y;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy / u_xlat2.xy;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat1.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[0].xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[2].xyz * u_xlat1.zzz + u_xlat1.xyw;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat0.xy + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat0.xy, u_xlat0.xy);
    u_xlat0.x = sqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 0.00100000005);
    u_xlat3.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat3.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat3.x);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xxx * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz / abs(u_xlat3.zzz);
    u_xlat10 = abs(_Offset) * 0.150000006;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat10;

    u_xlat6 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].w * u_xlat1.z + u_xlat6;
    u_xlat6 = u_xlat6 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].w;
    u_xlat0.xy = vec2(u_xlat6) * u_xlat0.xy;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy * vec2(0.00462962966, 0.00462962966);
    u_xlat2.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[0].x;
    u_xlat2.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[1].y;
    u_xlat0.xy = u_xlat0.xy / u_xlat2.xy;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat1.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[0].xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[2].xyz * u_xlat1.zzz + u_xlat1.xyw;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat0.xy + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat0.xy, u_xlat0.xy);
    u_xlat0.x = sqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 0.00100000005);
    u_xlat3.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat3.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat3.x);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xxx * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz / abs(u_xlat3.zzz);
    u_xlat10 = abs(_Offset) * 0.150000006;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * u_xlat10;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 100.0;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * u_xlat0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[0].z;
    u_xlat1.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[1].z;
    u_xlat1.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[2].z;
    u_xlat1.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[3].z;
    u_xlat0.w = 1.0;
    gl_Position.z = dot(u_xlat1, u_xlat0);
    u_xlat1.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[0].x;
    u_xlat1.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[2].x;
    u_xlat1.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[3].x;
    gl_Position.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat0.xzw);
    u_xlat1.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[1].y;
    u_xlat1.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[2].y;
    u_xlat1.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[3].y;
    gl_Position.y = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat0.yzw);
    u_xlat0.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[2].w;
    u_xlat0.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[3].w;
    gl_Position.w = dot(u_xlat0.xy, u_xlat0.zw);
    return;
}

#endif
#ifdef FRAGMENT
#version 100

#ifdef GL_FRAGMENT_PRECISION_HIGH
    precision highp float;
#else
    precision mediump float;
#endif
precision highp int;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
#define SV_Target0 gl_FragData[0]
void main()
{
    SV_Target0.xyz = max(vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz, vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0));
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}
SubProgram "gles3 " {
Keywords { "_VCOLOR2N_OFF" "_VTEX_ON" }

#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(binding = x, std140)

#define UNITY_LOCATION(x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(std140)

#endif

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _OutlineMap;
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump float vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
vec3 u_xlat3;
float u_xlat9;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0 = 0.0;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = max(u_xlat9, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat9 = dot(_lightDir.xyz, _lightDir.xyz);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat9) * _lightDir.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat0.x = min(max(u_xlat0.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat0.x = clamp(u_xlat0.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat3.xyz = (-_OutlineColor.xyz) + vec3(1.0, 1.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat3.xyz + _OutlineColor.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = textureLod(_OutlineMap, in_TEXCOORD0.xy, 0.0);
    vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat1.w * abs(_Offset);
    vs_TEXCOORD1.w = 1.0;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_NORMAL0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_NORMAL0.xxx + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_NORMAL0.zzz + u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xy = u_xlat3.yy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].xy;
    u_xlat3.xy = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].xy * u_xlat3.xx + u_xlat1.xy;
    u_xlat3.xy = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].xy * u_xlat3.zz + u_xlat3.xy;
    u_xlat9 = dot(u_xlat3.xy, u_xlat3.xy);
    u_xlat9 = inversesqrt(u_xlat9);
    u_xlat3.xy = vec2(u_xlat9) * u_xlat3.xy;
    u_xlat3.xy = u_xlat3.xy / _ScreenParams.xy;
    u_xlat3.xy = u_xlat3.xy * _ScreenResolution.yy;
    u_xlat1.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat1.y * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1].w;
    u_xlat9 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0].w * u_xlat1.x + u_xlat9;
    u_xlat9 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2].w * u_xlat1.z + u_xlat9;
    u_xlat9 = u_xlat9 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3].w;
    u_xlat0.yz = vec2(u_xlat9) * u_xlat3.xy;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * vec3(0.150000006, 0.00462962966, 0.00462962966);
    u_xlat2.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[0].x;
    u_xlat2.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[1].y;
    u_xlat3.xy = u_xlat0.yz / u_xlat2.xy;
    u_xlat2.xyz = u_xlat1.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[1].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[0].xyz * u_xlat1.xxx + u_xlat2.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[2].xyz * u_xlat1.zzz + u_xlat1.xyw;
    u_xlat1.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixV[3].xyz;

    u_xlat3.x = sqrt(u_xlat3.x);
    u_xlat3.x = max(u_xlat3.x, 0.00100000005);
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat3.x * u_xlat0.x;
    u_xlat0.x = u_xlat0.x * 100.0;
    u_xlat3.x = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat3.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat3.x);
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xxx * u_xlat1.xyz;

    u_xlat1.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[0].z;
    u_xlat1.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[1].z;
    u_xlat1.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[2].z;
    u_xlat1.w = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[3].z;
    u_xlat0.w = 1.0;
    gl_Position.z = dot(u_xlat1, u_xlat0);
    u_xlat1.x = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[0].x;
    u_xlat1.y = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[2].x;
    u_xlat1.z = hlslcc_mtx4x4glstate_matrix_projection[3].x;

uniform 	vec3 _LightDirection;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying highp vec2 vs_TEXCOORD0;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
float u_xlat6;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _BaseMap_ST.xy + _BaseMap_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.xyz = in_POSITION0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_POSITION0.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_POSITION0.zzz + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = _LightDirection.xyz * _ShadowBias.xxx + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat1.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat1.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat6 = dot(u_xlat1.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat6 = max(u_xlat6, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat6 = inversesqrt(u_xlat6);
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat6) * u_xlat1.xyz;
    u_xlat6 = dot(_LightDirection.xyz, u_xlat1.xyz);
    u_xlat6 = clamp(u_xlat6, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat6 = (-u_xlat6) + 1.0;
    u_xlat6 = u_xlat6 * _ShadowBias.y;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * vec3(u_xlat6) + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    gl_Position.z = max((-u_xlat0.w), u_xlat0.z);
    gl_Position.xyw = u_xlat0.xyw;
    return;
}

#endif
#ifdef FRAGMENT

    u_xlat6 = (-u_xlat6) + 1.0;
    u_xlat6 = u_xlat6 * _ShadowBias.y;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat1.xyz * vec3(u_xlat6) + u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1 = u_xlat0.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat1 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat0.xxxx + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat0.zzzz + u_xlat1;
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    gl_Position.z = max((-u_xlat0.w), u_xlat0.z);
    gl_Position.xyw = u_xlat0.xyw;
    return;
}

#endif
#ifdef FRAGMENT
#version 300 es

precision highp float;
precision highp int;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_TARGET0;
void main()
{
    SV_TARGET0 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    return;
}

#endif
"
}
}
